// â"€â"€ Theme â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

export struct ThemePalette {
    background: brush,
    sidebar: brush,
    card: brush,
    card-hover: brush,
    text: brush,
    text-muted: brush,
    accent: brush,
    accent-dim: brush,
    selection: brush,
    danger: brush,
    border: brush,
}

export global L10n {
    out property <string> app-name:          "Strata";
    out property <string> app-tagline:       "WALLPAPER ENGINE";
    out property <string> tab-library:       "Library";
    out property <string> tab-compositor:    "Compositor";
    out property <string> tab-parallax:      "Parallax Studio";
    out property <string> tab-settings:      "Settings";
    out property <string> tab-diagnostics:   "Diagnostics";
    out property <string> btn-quit:          "Quit";
    out property <string> btn-import:        "Import Wallpaper";
    out property <string> search-placeholder:"Search shaders and tags...";
    out property <string> no-wallpapers:     "No wallpapers found. Click Import to add one.";

    // Header titles + subtitles (mirrors the prototype's page.tsx header copy).
    out property <string> title-library:      "Wallpaper Library";
    out property <string> sub-library:        "Manage your high-fidelity motion assets and auto-tagged collections.";
    out property <string> title-compositor:   "Display Compositor";
    out property <string> sub-compositor:      "Intuitive layer stacking and cross-monitor spatial mapping.";
    out property <string> title-parallax:     "Parallax Studio";
    out property <string> sub-parallax:        "Create animated 3D parallax live wallpapers from images.";
    out property <string> title-diagnostics:  "Engine Diagnostics";
    out property <string> sub-diagnostics:     "Real-time telemetry and shader performance analysis.";
    out property <string> title-settings:     "Engine Settings";
    out property <string> sub-settings:        "Configure engine core and integration parameters.";
}

export global Theme {
    in property <bool>   is-dark: true;
    in property <string> mode:    "dark"; // "dark" | "light" | "system"

    // Typography tokens - registered at startup from assets/fonts/*.ttf.
    out property <string> font-headline: "Space Grotesk";
    out property <string> font-body:     "Inter";
    out property <string> font-code:     "Source Code Pro";

    // Palette ported 1:1 from the ui-prototype's HSL design system (globals.css),
    // converted to hex. Dark = "iOS Dark / Refined Grey", Light = "iOS Light".
    out property <ThemePalette> palette: root.is-dark ? {
        background:  #111317,
        sidebar:     #16191f,
        card:        #1e2229,
        card-hover:  #272b35,
        text:        #f9fafb,
        text-muted:  #94a3b8,
        accent:      #0a85ff,
        accent-dim:  #14385c,
        selection:   #10b981,
        danger:      #ba2c2c,
        border:      #2b303b,
    } : {
        background:  #f3f5f7,
        sidebar:     #e9edf1,
        card:        #ffffff,
        card-hover:  #f0f1f5,
        text:        #0f1729,
        text-muted:  #65758b,
        accent:      #0080ff,
        accent-dim:  #bfdbfe,
        selection:   #059669,
        danger:      #ef4343,
        border:      #cdd7e5,
    };
}

// Monitor "hardware color tag" → concrete color (matches the prototype's set).
export global MonColors {
    public pure function of(name: string) -> color {
        return name == "orange"  ? #f97316
             : name == "blue"    ? #3b82f6
             : name == "purple"  ? #a855f7
             : name == "emerald" ? #10b981
             : name == "rose"    ? #f43f5e
             : Theme.palette.accent;
    }
}

// â"€â"€ Shared data structs â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

export struct WallpaperItem {
    name:          string,
    author:        string,
    source-url:    string,   // original page (e.g. Shadertoy); empty if unknown
    tags:          [string],
    visible:       bool,
    has-thumbnail: bool,
    thumbnail:     image,
    usage-counts:  [int],
    is-selected:   bool,
    is-active:     bool,   // applied to at least one monitor
    is-parallax:   bool,   // shader vs parallax asset (badge)
    is-imported:   bool,   // imported from a Shadertoy export (red badge + delete)
    is-video:      bool,   // movie (.mp4) wallpaper (red film badge + delete)
}

export struct LayerItem {
    name:             string,
    opacity:          float,
    resolution-scale: float,
    positioning:      string,
    visible:          bool,
    blend-mode:       string,   // normal | additive | multiply
    is-video:         bool,     // .mp4 wallpaper: show Fit selector instead of Blend
    x: float, y: float, width: float, height: float,
}

export struct LogEntry {
    time:    string,
    level:   string,   // INFO | WARN | ERROR | DEBUG
    message: string,
}

export struct MonitorItem {
    id: string, name: string,
    color: string,   // orange | blue | purple | emerald | rose
    width: int, height: int,
    x: int, y: int,
}

export struct ToastData {
    id: int,
    title: string,
    description: string,
    destructive: bool,   // true → error styling (e.g. failed to apply shader)
}

// â"€â"€ Small reusable components â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

component Divider inherits Rectangle {
    height: 1px;
    background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff14 : #00000014;
}


component SidebarButton inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> text;
    in property <string> icon;
    in property <bool>   active;
    in property <bool>   danger: false;
    callback clicked();

    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: active ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.12)
              : (ta.has-hover ? (danger ? Theme.palette.danger.with-alpha(0.12)
                                        : (Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff0d : #00000008))
                              : transparent);
    animate background { duration: 250ms; easing: ease; }

    // Active accent bar on the left edge.
    Rectangle {
        x: 0; y: (parent.height - 24px) / 2;
        width: 3px; height: active ? 24px : 0px;
        border-radius: 2px;
        background: Theme.palette.accent;
        animate height { duration: 200ms; easing: ease-out; }
    }

    ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.clicked(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }

    HorizontalLayout {
        padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px; spacing: 12px; alignment: start;
        Icon {
            name: root.icon; size: 20px;
            color: active ? Theme.palette.accent
                 : (danger && ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.danger
                    : (ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.text : Theme.palette.text-muted));
            y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;
        }
        Text {
            text: root.text;
            color: active ? Theme.palette.accent
                 : (danger && ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.danger
                    : (ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.text : Theme.palette.text-muted));
            font-family: Theme.font-body;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: active ? 700 : 500;
            vertical-alignment: center;
        }
    }
}

component Toggle inherits Rectangle {
    in-out property <bool> checked;
    in property <bool> enabled: true;
    callback toggled(bool);

    width: 40px; height: 22px; border-radius: 11px;
    opacity: enabled ? 1.0 : 0.4;
    background: checked ? Theme.palette.accent : (Theme.is-dark ? #444450 : #c0c0cc);
    animate background { duration: 150ms; easing: ease; }

    Rectangle {
        x: checked ? 20px : 2px;
        y: 3px; width: 16px; height: 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #ffffff;
        drop-shadow-blur: checked ? 2px : 0px;
        drop-shadow-color: #00000044;
        animate x { duration: 150ms; easing: ease-in-out; }
    }
    TouchArea {
        clicked => { if (root.enabled) { root.checked = !root.checked; root.toggled(root.checked); } }
        mouse-cursor: root.enabled ? pointer : default;
    }
}


// Accent-colored slider with full control over the thumb position, so it can
// snap to discrete values (the std Slider can't be themed/snapped reliably).
// `value` is display-only (driven by the parent); drags emit `changed(raw)`.
component AccentSlider inherits Rectangle {
    in property <float> minimum: 0;
    in property <float> maximum: 100;
    in property <float> value: 0;
    callback changed(float);

    height: 24px;
    property <length> thumb-size: 18px;
    property <float> ratio: (root.maximum - root.minimum) > 0
        ? Math.max(0, Math.min(1, (root.value - root.minimum) / (root.maximum - root.minimum)))
        : 0;

    function set-from-x(mx: length) {
        root.changed(root.minimum + Math.max(0, Math.min(1, mx / root.width)) * (root.maximum - root.minimum));
    }

    // Track + filled portion
    Rectangle {
        y: (parent.height - 6px) / 2;
        height: 6px; border-radius: 3px;
        background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff1f : #00000017;
        Rectangle {
            x: 0; y: 0; height: 100%;
            width: parent.width * root.ratio;
            border-radius: 3px;
            background: Theme.palette.accent;
        }
    }
    // Thumb
    Rectangle {
        width: thumb-size; height: thumb-size; border-radius: thumb-size / 2;
        x: (root.width - thumb-size) * root.ratio;
        y: (parent.height - thumb-size) / 2;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-width: 2px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent;
        drop-shadow-blur: 4px; drop-shadow-color: #00000040;
    }
    ta := TouchArea {
        mouse-cursor: pointer;
        moved => { if (self.pressed) { root.set-from-x(self.mouse-x); } }
        pointer-event(e) => {
            if (e.button == PointerEventButton.left && e.kind == PointerEventKind.down) {
                root.set-from-x(self.mouse-x);
            }
        }
    }
}

// â"€â"€ Settings building blocks â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

// Single-line text input styled to match the app (blue focus accent), instead of
// the std-widgets LineEdit whose accent (pink) can't be retinted via Palette.
component BlueInput inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> placeholder;
    in-out property <string> text <=> ti.text;
    height: 44px; border-radius: 10px;
    background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff0c : #00000008;
    border-width: 1.5px;
    border-color: ti.has-focus ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.border;
    forward-focus: ti;
    animate border-color { duration: 120ms; }
    HorizontalLayout {
        padding-left: 12px; padding-right: 12px;
        ti := TextInput {
            vertical-alignment: center;
            color: Theme.palette.text;
            font-size: 14px;
            single-line: true;
            selection-background-color: Theme.palette.accent;
        }
    }
    if ti.text == "" : Text {
        x: 12px; height: 100%; vertical-alignment: center;
        text: root.placeholder;
        color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
}

// Uppercase tracked section heading with an accent icon (matches the prototype).
component SectionLabel inherits HorizontalLayout {
    in property <string> text;
    in property <string> icon;
    spacing: 10px; alignment: start;
    Icon { name: root.icon; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
    Text {
        text: root.text;
        color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
        font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 3px;
        vertical-alignment: center;
    }
}

// Solid rounded panel (the prototype's glass-panel → solid card, no fake blur).
component SettingsPanel inherits Rectangle {
    in property <bool> disabled: false;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: Theme.palette.card;
    border-width: 1px;
    border-color: Theme.palette.border;
    opacity: disabled ? 0.5 : 1.0;
    VerticalLayout {
        padding: 28px; spacing: 22px;
        @children
    }
}

// Theme-mode pick button (icon over/with label, active = accent ring + tint).
component ThemeModeButton inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> text;
    in property <string> icon;
    in property <bool>   active;
    callback clicked();
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border-width: 2px;
    border-color: active ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.border;
    background: active ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.08)
              : (ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent);
    animate border-color, background { duration: 150ms; }
    HorizontalLayout {
        alignment: center; spacing: 10px;
        Icon { name: root.icon; size: 18px; color: active ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
        Text {
            text: root.text;
            color: active ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text;
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; vertical-alignment: center;
        }
    }
    ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.clicked(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
}

// Custom dropdown select (rounded card field + popup list) to match the prototype.
component Select inherits Rectangle {
    in property <[string]> options;
    in-out property <string> current;
    callback selected(string);
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: Theme.palette.card;
    border-width: 1px;
    border-color: sel-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.border;
    animate border-color { duration: 150ms; }
    HorizontalLayout {
        padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 14px; spacing: 8px;
        Text {
            text: root.current; color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
            vertical-alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1; overflow: elide;
        }
        Icon { name: "chevron-down"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
    }
    sel-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { opt-popup.show(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
    opt-popup := PopupWindow {
        x: 0; y: parent.height + 6px; width: root.width;
        Rectangle {
            background: Theme.palette.card;
            border-radius: 12px; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
            drop-shadow-blur: 30px; drop-shadow-color: #00000066;
            VerticalLayout {
                padding: 6px; spacing: 2px;
                for opt in root.options : Rectangle {
                    height: 40px; border-radius: 9px;
                    background: opt-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.12)
                              : (opt == root.current ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.06) : transparent);
                    HorizontalLayout {
                        padding-left: 12px; padding-right: 12px; spacing: 8px;
                        Text {
                            text: opt; color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 13px;
                            font-weight: opt == root.current ? 700 : 500;
                            vertical-alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1;
                        }
                        if opt == root.current : Icon { name: "check"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    }
                    opt-ta := TouchArea {
                        clicked => { root.current = opt; root.selected(opt); }
                        mouse-cursor: pointer;
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

// â"€â"€ Settings sections (each = SectionLabel + SettingsPanel) â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
// Extracted into components so the Settings tab can reflow between a two-column
// (wide) and single-column (narrow) layout without duplicating the markup.

component AppearanceSettings inherits VerticalLayout {
    callback theme-changed(string);
    spacing: 16px;
    SectionLabel { icon: "palette"; text: "GENERAL APPEARANCE"; }
    SettingsPanel {
        Text { text: "Theme Mode"; font-family: Theme.font-headline; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 12px;
            ThemeModeButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; icon: "sun"; text: "Light"; active: Theme.mode == "light"; clicked => { Theme.mode = "light"; root.theme-changed("light"); } }
            ThemeModeButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; icon: "moon"; text: "Dark"; active: Theme.mode == "dark"; clicked => { Theme.mode = "dark"; root.theme-changed("dark"); } }
            ThemeModeButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; icon: "laptop"; text: "System"; active: Theme.mode == "system"; clicked => { Theme.mode = "system"; root.theme-changed("system"); } }
        }
        Divider {}
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 16px;
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 4px;
                Text { text: "Adaptive UI Color Sync"; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "Automatically synchronize UI theme with active wallpaper chroma. (Coming soon)"; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; wrap: word-wrap; }
            }
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Toggle { checked: false; enabled: false; } }
        }
    }
}

component IntegrationsSettings inherits VerticalLayout {
    spacing: 16px;
    HorizontalLayout {
        spacing: 8px;
        SectionLabel { icon: "puzzle"; text: "INTEGRATIONS"; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
        // UPCOMING - integrations are planned, hence the panel is greyed/disabled.
        Rectangle {
            height: 20px; width: int-up.preferred-width + 18px; border-radius: 6px;
            background: Theme.palette.card-hover;
            y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;
            int-up := Text { text: "UPCOMING"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800;
                             letter-spacing: 2px; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
        }
    }
    SettingsPanel {
        disabled: true;
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 4px;
            Text { text: "Spotify API Integration"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
            Text { text: "Audio reactive shaders based on playback."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
        }
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 8px;
            Rectangle {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
                background: Theme.palette.background; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                Text { x: 16px; text: "Enter Client Secret / API Key..."; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 13px; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
            Rectangle {
                width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; background: Theme.palette.card-hover;
                Icon { name: "save"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
            }
        }
        Divider {}
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 4px;
            Text { text: "Steam Profile"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
            Text { text: "Show profile stats and games owned on wallpapers."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
        }
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 8px;
            Rectangle {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
                background: Theme.palette.background; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                Text { x: 16px; text: "USERNAME"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 13px; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
            Rectangle {
                width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; background: Theme.palette.card-hover;
                Icon { name: "save"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
            }
        }
        Divider {}
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 16px;
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 4px;
                Text { text: "Discord Rich Presence"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "Display active wallpaper status on your profile."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
            }
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Toggle { checked: false; enabled: false; } }
        }
    }
}

component SystemControlSettings inherits VerticalLayout {
    in property <bool>   autostart;
    in property <bool>   disable-mpo;
    in property <int>    fps-cap;
    in property <string> shader-quality;
    in property <string> vsync-mode;
    callback autostart-toggled(bool);
    callback mpo-toggled(bool);
    callback fps-cap-changed(int);
    callback shader-quality-changed(string);
    callback vsync-changed(string);

    pure function snap-fps(v: float) -> int {
        return Math.abs(v - 30) <= 3 ? 30
             : Math.abs(v - 60) <= 3 ? 60
             : Math.abs(v - 90) <= 3 ? 90
             : Math.abs(v - 120) <= 3 ? 120
             : Math.round(v);
    }

    spacing: 16px;
    SectionLabel { icon: "settings-2"; text: "SYSTEM CONTROL"; }
    SettingsPanel {
        // Launch at Startup
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 16px;
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 4px;
                Text { text: "Launch at Startup"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "Auto-start the engine when system boots."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
            }
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Toggle { checked: root.autostart; toggled(v) => { root.autostart-toggled(v); } } }
        }
        Divider {}
        // Disable MPO (Multi-Plane Overlay)
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 16px;
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 4px;
                Text { text: "Disable MPO (Multi-Plane Overlay)"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "For NVIDIA users who experience black screenshots or overlay flicker. Can affect FreeSync / G-Sync. Requires admin privileges and a system restart to change."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; wrap: word-wrap; }
            }
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Toggle { checked: root.disable-mpo; toggled(v) => { root.mpo-toggled(v); } } }
        }
        Divider {}
        // Target FPS
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 16px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                HorizontalLayout {
                    horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 8px; alignment: start;
                    Icon { name: "activity"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    Text { text: "Target FPS"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
                Rectangle {
                    height: 22px; width: fps-b.preferred-width + 18px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.25);
                    fps-b := Text { text: root.fps-cap + " FPS"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
            AccentSlider {
                minimum: 1; maximum: 144; value: root.fps-cap;
                changed(v) => { root.fps-cap-changed(root.snap-fps(v)); }
            }
            HorizontalLayout {
                Text { text: "1 FPS"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
                Text { text: "30"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; color: root.fps-cap == 30 ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Rectangle { width: 12px; }
                Text { text: "60"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; color: root.fps-cap == 60 ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Rectangle { width: 12px; }
                Text { text: "90"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; color: root.fps-cap == 90 ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Rectangle { width: 12px; }
                Text { text: "120"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; color: root.fps-cap == 120 ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Text { text: "144 FPS"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; horizontal-stretch: 1; horizontal-alignment: right; }
            }
        }
        Divider {}
        // Shader Quality - global render-scale preset (Low/Medium/High).
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 12px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 8px; alignment: start;
                Icon { name: "zap"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                Text { text: "Shader Quality"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
            Select {
                options: ["Low (Performance Mode)", "Medium (Balanced)", "High (Maximum Fidelity)"];
                current: root.shader-quality;
                selected(v) => { root.shader-quality-changed(v); }
            }
        }
        Divider {}
        // V-Sync Mode
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 12px;
            Text { text: "V-Sync Mode"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
            Select {
                options: ["Fifo (VSync On)", "Immediate (VSync Off)", "Mailbox (Ultra-Fast)"];
                current: root.vsync-mode;
                selected(v) => { root.vsync-changed(v); }
            }
        }
    }
}

// Audio + mouse interactivity controls, grouped into one section.
component InteractivitySettings inherits VerticalLayout {
    in property <float> audio-sensitivity;
    in property <string> mouse-mode;   // Off | On (Everything) | On (Only Shaders) | On (Only Parallax Studio)
    in property <float> mouse-sensitivity;
    callback audio-sensitivity-changed(float);
    callback mouse-mode-changed(string);
    callback mouse-sensitivity-changed(float);

    spacing: 16px;
    SectionLabel { icon: "activity"; text: "INTERACTIVITY"; }
    SettingsPanel {
        // ── Audio Sensitivity ──
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 12px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                HorizontalLayout {
                    horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 8px; alignment: start;
                    Icon { name: "activity"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    Text { text: "Audio Sensitivity"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
                Rectangle {
                    height: 22px; width: arst-txt.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: arst-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : Theme.palette.card;
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                    arst-txt := Text { text: "Reset"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;
                                      horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                    arst-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.audio-sensitivity-changed(1.0); } }
                }
                Rectangle {
                    height: 22px; width: aud-b.preferred-width + 18px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.25);
                    aud-b := Text { text: Math.round(root.audio-sensitivity * 100) + "%"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
            Text { text: "How strongly wallpapers react to system audio."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
            AccentSlider {
                minimum: 0; maximum: 300; value: root.audio-sensitivity * 100;
                changed(v) => { root.audio-sensitivity-changed(v / 100); }
            }
        }
        Divider {}
        // ── Mouse Interactivity mode ──
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 16px;
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 4px;
                Text { text: "Mouse Interactivity"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "Which wallpapers follow the cursor. Parallax Studio wallpapers drift on their own when not interactive."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; wrap: word-wrap; }
            }
            VerticalLayout {
                alignment: center; min-width: 200px;
                Select {
                    options: ["Off", "On (Everything)", "On (Only Shaders)", "On (Only Parallax Studio)"];
                    current: root.mouse-mode;
                    selected(v) => { root.mouse-mode-changed(v); }
                }
            }
        }
        // ── Mouse Sensitivity (only relevant when not Off) ──
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 12px;
            opacity: root.mouse-mode != "Off" ? 1.0 : 0.45;
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                HorizontalLayout {
                    horizontal-stretch: 1; spacing: 8px; alignment: start;
                    Icon { name: "move"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    Text { text: "Mouse Sensitivity"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
                Rectangle {
                    height: 22px; width: mrst-txt.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: mrst-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : Theme.palette.card;
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                    mrst-txt := Text { text: "Reset"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;
                                      horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                    mrst-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { if (root.mouse-mode != "Off") { root.mouse-sensitivity-changed(1.0); } } }
                }
                Rectangle {
                    height: 22px; width: ms-b.preferred-width + 18px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.25);
                    ms-b := Text { text: Math.round(root.mouse-sensitivity * 100) + "%"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
            AccentSlider {
                minimum: 10; maximum: 400; value: root.mouse-sensitivity * 100;
                changed(v) => { if (root.mouse-mode != "Off") { root.mouse-sensitivity-changed(v / 100); } }
            }
        }
    }
}

component UpdatesSettings inherits VerticalLayout {
    spacing: 16px;
    // Driven from Rust: the engine-version badge text, the action-button label
    // ("CHECK FOR UPDATES" / "CHECKING…" / "DOWNLOAD UPDATE"), whether a newer
    // release was found (changes the accent), and a busy flag. `update-clicked`
    // is handled in Rust (it either runs the check or opens the releases page).
    in property <string> version-badge: "v1.1.0 (LATEST)";
    in property <string> update-button-label: "CHECK FOR UPDATES";
    in property <bool> update-available;
    in property <bool> update-checking;
    callback update-clicked();
    // Asset Library (Strata-Library) - mirrors the engine row.
    in property <string> lib-version-badge: "v1.1.0 (LATEST)";
    in property <string> lib-update-button-label: "CHECK FOR UPDATES";
    in property <bool> lib-update-available;
    in property <bool> lib-update-checking;
    callback lib-update-clicked();
    SectionLabel { icon: "arrow-up-circle"; text: "UPDATES"; }
    SettingsPanel {
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 8px;
            Text { text: "Strata Engine"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; vertical-alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
            Rectangle {
                height: 20px; width: ver-b.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
                background: (root.update-available ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.selection).with-alpha(0.12);
                ver-b := Text { text: root.version-badge; color: root.update-available ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.selection; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
        }
        Rectangle {
            height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; border-width: 1px;
            border-color: root.update-available ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.5) : Theme.palette.border;
            background: root.update-available
                ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(upd-ta.has-hover ? 0.18 : 0.10)
                : (upd-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.text.with-alpha(0.05) : transparent);
            opacity: root.update-checking ? 0.5 : 1.0;
            animate background { duration: 150ms; }
            Text { text: root.update-button-label; color: root.update-available ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
            upd-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { if (!root.update-checking) { root.update-clicked(); } } mouse-cursor: root.update-checking ? default : pointer; }
        }
        Divider {}
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 8px;
            Text { text: "Asset Library"; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; vertical-alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
            Rectangle {
                height: 20px; width: lib-b.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
                background: (root.lib-update-available ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.selection).with-alpha(0.12);
                lib-b := Text { text: root.lib-version-badge; color: root.lib-update-available ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.selection; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
        }
        Rectangle {
            height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; border-width: 1px;
            border-color: root.lib-update-available ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.5) : Theme.palette.border;
            background: root.lib-update-available
                ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(lib-ta.has-hover ? 0.18 : 0.10)
                : (lib-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.text.with-alpha(0.05) : transparent);
            opacity: root.lib-update-checking ? 0.5 : 1.0;
            animate background { duration: 150ms; }
            Text { text: root.lib-update-button-label; color: root.lib-update-available ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
            lib-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { if (!root.lib-update-checking) { root.lib-update-clicked(); } } mouse-cursor: root.lib-update-checking ? default : pointer; }
        }
    }
}

// â"€â"€ Diagnostics building blocks â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

// A telemetry stat tile: icon chip + optional status badge, big value at bottom.
component StatCard inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> icon;
    in property <brush>  icon-bg;
    in property <brush>  icon-color;
    in property <string> label;
    in property <string> value;
    in property <string> unit;
    in property <brush>  value-color: Theme.palette.text;
    in property <string> badge;
    in property <brush>  badge-color: Theme.palette.selection;

    height: 150px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: Theme.palette.card;
    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
    drop-shadow-blur: 14px; drop-shadow-color: #00000022; drop-shadow-offset-y: 4px;

    VerticalLayout {
        padding: 24px; spacing: 0;
        HorizontalLayout {
            alignment: space-between;
            Rectangle {
                width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px; background: icon-bg;
                Icon { name: root.icon; size: 20px; color: root.icon-color; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
            }
            if root.badge != "" : Rectangle {
                height: 20px; width: badge-txt.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
                background: root.badge-color.with-alpha(0.12);
                y: 0;
                badge-txt := Text { text: root.badge; color: root.badge-color; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px;
                       horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
        }
        Rectangle { vertical-stretch: 1; }
        VerticalLayout {
            spacing: 4px;
            Text { text: root.label; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; }
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 6px; alignment: start;
                Text { text: root.value; font-family: Theme.font-headline; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: root.value-color; }
                if root.unit != "" : Text { text: root.unit; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; vertical-alignment: bottom; }
            }
        }
    }
}

// Colored severity chip for a log line.
component LogLevelBadge inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> level;
    property <brush> c: root.level == "ERROR" ? Theme.palette.danger
                      : root.level == "WARN"  ? #f59e0b
                      : root.level == "DEBUG" ? #38bdf8
                      : Theme.palette.accent;
    height: 16px; width: lvl-txt.preferred-width + 12px; border-radius: 4px;
    background: c.with-alpha(0.14);
    lvl-txt := Text { text: root.level; color: root.c; font-size: 8px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px;
           horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
}

// FPS stat tile with live status badge (encapsulates the thresholds once so the
// responsive 4-up / 2x2 layouts don't duplicate the logic).
component FpsStatCard inherits StatCard {
    in property <float> fps;
    in property <bool> active: true;
    icon: "zap";
    icon-bg: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
    icon-color: Theme.palette.accent;
    label: "FPS";
    value: root.active ? "\{Math.round(root.fps)}" : "-";
    value-color: !root.active ? Theme.palette.text-muted
               : root.fps >= 50 ? Theme.palette.selection : root.fps >= 25 ? #f59e0b : Theme.palette.danger;
    badge: !root.active ? "INACTIVE" : root.fps >= 50 ? "STABLE" : root.fps >= 25 ? "FAIR" : "LOW";
    badge-color: !root.active ? Theme.palette.text-muted
               : root.fps >= 50 ? Theme.palette.selection : root.fps >= 25 ? #f59e0b : Theme.palette.danger;
}

// Shader Debugger + Debug Overlay actions tile.
component DebugActionsCard inherits Rectangle {
    in property <bool> debug-overlay;
    callback open-debugger();
    callback debug-toggled(bool);

    height: 150px; border-radius: 24px;
    background: Theme.palette.card; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
    drop-shadow-blur: 14px; drop-shadow-color: #00000022; drop-shadow-offset-y: 4px;
    VerticalLayout {
        padding: 20px; spacing: 14px; alignment: center;
        Rectangle {
            height: 44px; border-radius: 12px; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
            background: dbg-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
            animate background { duration: 150ms; }
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: center; spacing: 8px;
                Icon { name: "search-code"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.text; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                Text { text: "SHADER DEBUGGER"; color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
            dbg-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.open-debugger(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
        }
        HorizontalLayout {
            alignment: space-between;
            Text { text: "DEBUG OVERLAY"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Toggle { checked: root.debug-overlay; toggled(v) => { root.debug-toggled(v); } } }
        }
    }
}

// â"€â"€ WallpaperCard â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

// ── Compositor building blocks ──────────────────────────────────────────────

component SqBtn inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> icon;
    in property <bool> danger: false;
    callback clicked();
    width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 8px;
    background: ta.has-hover ? (danger ? Theme.palette.danger.with-alpha(0.15) : Theme.palette.card-hover) : transparent;
    animate background { duration: 120ms; }
    Icon { name: root.icon; size: 15px;
           color: danger && ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.danger : Theme.palette.text-muted;
           x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
    ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.clicked(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
}

component MiniBtn inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> icon;
    callback clicked();
    width: 22px; height: 15px; border-radius: 4px;
    background: ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
    Icon { name: root.icon; size: 11px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
           x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
    ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.clicked(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
}

// Spatial monitor canvas - positions each display to scale, supports select,
// per-monitor rename/color, refresh, and the span switch.
component CompositorCanvas inherits Rectangle {
    in property <[MonitorItem]> monitors;
    in property <int>  selected-index;
    in property <bool> span;
    in property <int>  canvas-min-x;
    in property <int>  canvas-min-y;
    in property <int>  canvas-max-x;
    in property <int>  canvas-max-y;
    // Spatial edit mode: layer index being edited (-1 = off) + draft box (monitor px).
    in-out property <int>   editing-layer: -1;
    in-out property <float> edit-x;
    in-out property <float> edit-y;
    in-out property <float> edit-w;
    in-out property <float> edit-h;
    callback monitor-selected(int);
    callback refresh();
    callback span-toggled(bool);
    callback rename(int, string);
    callback color-changed(int, string);
    callback edit-save();
    callback edit-cancel();
    callback edit-live();

    property <bool> editing: root.editing-layer >= 0 && root.selected-index >= 0;

    // Theme-aware canvas chrome colors. The stage flips dark↔light, so its text,
    // icons, chips and borders must flip too or they vanish (white-on-light).
    property <color> fg:           Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff   : #1a1f2b;
    property <color> fg-muted:     Theme.is-dark ? #ffffffaa : #5b6473;
    property <color> fg-faint:     Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff55 : #00000066;
    property <color> chip-bg:      Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff12 : #00000010;
    property <color> chip-bg-hover:Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff22 : #0000001c;
    property <color> chip-border:  Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff1a : #00000018;
    property <color> tile-border:  Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff24 : #00000022;
    property <color> tile-bg:      Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff08 : #00000008;

    border-radius: 24px;
    // Dark "stage" in dark mode; a light neutral surface in light mode so the
    // spatial canvas matches the theme instead of always being black.
    background: Theme.is-dark ? #0a0d13 : #e6eaf1;
    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
    clip: true;

    property <int> tw: Math.max(1, root.canvas-max-x - root.canvas-min-x);
    property <int> th: Math.max(1, root.canvas-max-y - root.canvas-min-y);
    property <float> scale: Math.min((self.width - 120px) / (root.tw * 1px), (self.height - 150px) / (root.th * 1px));
    property <length> x0: (self.width  - root.tw * root.scale * 1px) / 2;
    property <length> y0: (self.height - root.th * root.scale * 1px) / 2;

    // Single-monitor framing used while editing a layer's spatial box.
    property <int> msel-w: root.selected-index >= 0 ? root.monitors[root.selected-index].width  : 1;
    property <int> msel-h: root.selected-index >= 0 ? root.monitors[root.selected-index].height : 1;
    property <float> em-scale: Math.min((self.width - 120px) / (root.msel-w * 1px), (self.height - 150px) / (root.msel-h * 1px));
    property <length> em-x0: (self.width  - root.msel-w * root.em-scale * 1px) / 2;
    property <length> em-y0: (self.height - root.msel-h * root.em-scale * 1px) / 2;

    for m[i] in root.monitors : Rectangle {
        visible: !root.editing;
        property <color> mc: root.span && root.monitors.length > 0 ? MonColors.of(root.monitors[0].color) : MonColors.of(m.color);
        property <bool> active: root.span ? true : (root.selected-index == i);
        x: root.x0 + (m.x - root.canvas-min-x) * root.scale * 1px;
        y: root.y0 + (m.y - root.canvas-min-y) * root.scale * 1px;
        width:  m.width  * root.scale * 1px;
        height: m.height * root.scale * 1px;
        border-radius: 10px; border-width: 2px;
        border-color: active ? mc : root.tile-border;
        background: active ? mc.with-alpha(0.18) : root.tile-bg;
        drop-shadow-blur: active ? 26px : 0px; drop-shadow-color: mc.with-alpha(0.35);
        animate border-color, background, drop-shadow-blur { duration: 180ms; }

        TouchArea { clicked => { if (!root.span) { root.monitor-selected(i); } } mouse-cursor: root.span ? default : pointer; }

        VerticalLayout {
            alignment: center; spacing: 5px;
            HorizontalLayout { alignment: center; Icon { name: "monitor"; size: 28px; color: active ? mc : root.fg-muted; } }
            // Persistent display-number badge (shown regardless of custom name).
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: active ? mc.with-alpha(0.25) : root.chip-bg;
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: active ? mc : root.chip-border;
                    Text { text: i + 1; color: active ? root.fg : root.fg-muted; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
                           horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
            Text { text: m.name; color: active ? root.fg : root.fg-muted; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; horizontal-alignment: center; overflow: elide; }
            Text { text: m.width + " x " + m.height; color: root.fg-faint; font-size: 9px; horizontal-alignment: center; }
        }

        if !root.span : Rectangle {
            x: parent.width - 30px; y: 8px; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px;
            background: ed-ta.has-hover ? #ffffff2e : #00000055;
            Icon { name: "pencil"; size: 12px; color: #ffffffcc; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
            ed-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { mon-pop.show(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
            mon-pop := PopupWindow {
                x: -188px; y: 26px; width: 220px;
                // Don't close when the user clicks the name field inside the popup.
                close-policy: PopupClosePolicy.close-on-click-outside;
                Rectangle {
                    background: Theme.palette.card; border-radius: 14px; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                    drop-shadow-blur: 30px; drop-shadow-color: #00000088;
                    VerticalLayout {
                        padding: 12px; spacing: 10px;
                        Text { text: "CONFIGURE DISPLAY " + (i + 1); color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; }
                        Rectangle {
                            height: 38px; border-radius: 10px; clip: true;
                            background: Theme.palette.background; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                            name-in := TextInput {
                                x: 12px; width: parent.width - 24px; height: 100%;
                                vertical-alignment: center; single-line: true;
                                color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 13px;
                                text: m.name;
                                edited => { root.rename(i, self.text); }
                            }
                        }
                        HorizontalLayout {
                            spacing: 8px; alignment: start;
                            for c in ["orange", "blue", "purple", "emerald", "rose"] : Rectangle {
                                width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px;
                                background: MonColors.of(c);
                                border-width: 2px;
                                border-color: m.color == c ? #ffffff : transparent;
                                TouchArea { clicked => { root.color-changed(i, c); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // Top-left badge
    Rectangle {
        visible: !root.editing;
        x: 16px; y: 16px; height: 24px; width: badge-t.preferred-width + 24px; border-radius: 12px;
        background: root.chip-bg; border-width: 1px; border-color: root.chip-border;
        badge-t := Text { text: "SPATIAL CANVAS"; color: root.fg-muted; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 3px;
               horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
    }

    // Top-right refresh
    Rectangle {
        visible: !root.editing;
        x: parent.width - rf-row.preferred-width - 44px; y: 16px;
        height: 36px; width: rf-row.preferred-width + 28px; border-radius: 10px;
        background: rf-ta.has-hover ? root.chip-bg-hover : root.chip-bg; border-width: 1px; border-color: root.chip-border;
        animate background { duration: 150ms; }
        rf-row := HorizontalLayout {
            padding-left: 12px; padding-right: 12px; spacing: 8px; alignment: center;
            Icon { name: "refresh-cw"; size: 14px; color: root.fg-muted; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
            Text { text: "REFRESH MONITORS"; color: root.fg; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
        }
        rf-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.refresh(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
    }

    // Bottom-right span switch
    Rectangle {
        visible: !root.editing;
        x: parent.width - 250px; y: parent.height - 72px;
        width: 234px; height: 54px; border-radius: 14px;
        background: root.chip-bg; border-width: 1px; border-color: root.chip-border;
        HorizontalLayout {
            padding-left: 14px; padding-right: 14px; spacing: 10px;
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; alignment: center; spacing: 2px;
                Text { text: "SPAN MONITORS"; color: root.fg; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; }
                Text { text: "Treat displays as one canvas"; color: root.fg-muted; font-size: 8px; }
            }
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Toggle { checked: root.span; toggled(v) => { root.span-toggled(v); } } }
        }
    }

    // â”€â”€ Spatial edit overlay â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
    // Framed monitor (visual backdrop only; clipped to itself).
    if root.editing : Rectangle {
        x: root.em-x0; y: root.em-y0;
        width: root.msel-w * root.em-scale * 1px;
        height: root.msel-h * root.em-scale * 1px;
        border-radius: 8px; border-width: 2px; border-color: #ffffff30;
        background: #ffffff08;
        clip: true;
    }

    // Bounding box - a SIBLING of the frame (canvas coords) so it always renders
    // on top and is never clipped, even when the frame fills a maximized window.
    if root.editing : Rectangle {
        x: root.em-x0 + root.edit-x * root.em-scale * 1px;
        y: root.em-y0 + root.edit-y * root.em-scale * 1px;
        width:  root.edit-w * root.em-scale * 1px;
        height: root.edit-h * root.em-scale * 1px;
        border-width: 2px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent;
        background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.20);
        Rectangle {
            x: 0; y: -22px; height: 18px; width: sz-t.preferred-width + 12px; border-radius: 4px;
            background: Theme.palette.accent;
            sz-t := Text { text: Math.round(root.edit-w) + " x " + Math.round(root.edit-h);
                   color: #ffffff; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
        }
        HorizontalLayout { alignment: center; Icon { name: "move"; size: 18px; color: #ffffffcc; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; } }
        Rectangle {
            x: parent.width - 12px; y: parent.height - 12px; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 12px;
            background: Theme.palette.accent; border-width: 2px; border-color: #ffffff;
            drop-shadow-blur: 6px; drop-shadow-color: #00000066;
            Icon { name: "maximize"; size: 12px; color: #ffffff; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
        }
    }

    // Input layer over the frame (canvas coords; hit-tests in frame-local space).
    if root.editing : edit-ta := TouchArea {
        x: root.em-x0; y: root.em-y0;
        width: root.msel-w * root.em-scale * 1px;
        height: root.msel-h * root.em-scale * 1px;
        property <int> mode: 0;        // 0 none, 1 move, 2 resize
        property <float> sx;
        property <float> sy;
        property <float> ddx: (self.mouse-x - self.pressed-x) / 1px / root.em-scale;
        property <float> ddy: (self.mouse-y - self.pressed-y) / 1px / root.em-scale;
        mouse-cursor: pointer;
        pointer-event(e) => {
            if (e.kind == PointerEventKind.down) {
                if (self.mouse-x > (root.edit-x + root.edit-w) * root.em-scale * 1px - 20px
                    && self.mouse-y > (root.edit-y + root.edit-h) * root.em-scale * 1px - 20px) {
                    self.mode = 2; self.sx = root.edit-w; self.sy = root.edit-h;
                } else if (self.mouse-x > root.edit-x * root.em-scale * 1px
                        && self.mouse-x < (root.edit-x + root.edit-w) * root.em-scale * 1px
                        && self.mouse-y > root.edit-y * root.em-scale * 1px
                        && self.mouse-y < (root.edit-y + root.edit-h) * root.em-scale * 1px) {
                    self.mode = 1; self.sx = root.edit-x; self.sy = root.edit-y;
                } else {
                    self.mode = 0;
                }
            }
            if (e.kind == PointerEventKind.up) { self.mode = 0; }
        }
        moved => {
            if (self.pressed && self.mode == 1) {
                root.edit-x = Math.max(0, Math.min(root.msel-w - root.edit-w, self.sx + self.ddx));
                root.edit-y = Math.max(0, Math.min(root.msel-h - root.edit-h, self.sy + self.ddy));
                root.edit-live();
            } else if (self.pressed && self.mode == 2) {
                root.edit-w = Math.max(100, Math.min(root.msel-w - root.edit-x, self.sx + self.ddx));
                root.edit-h = Math.max(100, Math.min(root.msel-h - root.edit-y, self.sy + self.ddy));
                root.edit-live();
            }
        }
    }

    // Edit toolbar (Save / Discard) - buttons vertically centered in the bar.
    if root.editing : Rectangle {
        x: (parent.width - tb-row.preferred-width - 32px) / 2; y: parent.height - 66px;
        height: 46px; width: tb-row.preferred-width + 32px; border-radius: 14px;
        background: Theme.palette.card; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
        drop-shadow-blur: 24px; drop-shadow-color: #00000066;
        tb-row := HorizontalLayout {
            padding-left: 12px; padding-right: 12px; spacing: 10px; alignment: center;
            VerticalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    height: 32px; width: cx-t.preferred-width + 28px; border-radius: 9px;
                    background: cx-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                    HorizontalLayout { alignment: center; spacing: 6px;
                        Icon { name: "x"; size: 13px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                        cx-t := Text { text: "DISCARD"; color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
                    }
                    cx-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.edit-cancel(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                }
            }
            VerticalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    height: 32px; width: sv-t.preferred-width + 28px; border-radius: 9px;
                    background: sv-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.brighter(0.12) : Theme.palette.accent;
                    HorizontalLayout { alignment: center; spacing: 6px;
                        Icon { name: "save"; size: 13px; color: #ffffff; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                        sv-t := Text { text: "SAVE GEOMETRY"; color: #ffffff; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
                    }
                    sv-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.edit-save(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

// Per-monitor shader layer stack (right panel).
// The stacked layer cards (no scroll of its own - the host decides).
component LayerList inherits VerticalLayout {
    in property <[LayerItem]> layers;
    callback move-up(int);
    callback move-down(int);
    callback remove(int);
    callback opacity-changed(int, float);
    callback blend-changed(int, string);
    callback positioning-changed(int, string);
    callback visibility-toggled(int, bool);
    callback edit-requested(int);

    spacing: 12px; alignment: start;
    for layer[i] in root.layers : Rectangle {
        background: Theme.palette.card; border-radius: 16px; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
        VerticalLayout {
            padding: 14px; spacing: 14px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 4px;
                Text { text: layer.name; color: layer.visible ? Theme.palette.text : Theme.palette.text-muted;
                       font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1; overflow: elide; }
                VerticalLayout {
                    alignment: center; spacing: 1px;
                    MiniBtn { icon: "chevron-up";   clicked => { root.move-up(i); } }
                    MiniBtn { icon: "chevron-down"; clicked => { root.move-down(i); } }
                }
                SqBtn { icon: "pencil"; clicked => { root.edit-requested(i); } }
                SqBtn { icon: layer.visible ? "eye" : "eye-off"; clicked => { root.visibility-toggled(i, !layer.visible); } }
                SqBtn { icon: "trash-2"; danger: true; clicked => { root.remove(i); } }
            }
            // Video wallpapers don't blend like shaders - they get a fit/scaling mode
            // instead. Shaders keep the traditional blend-mode control.
            if layer.is-video : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 6px;
                Text { text: "FIT MODE"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 8px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; }
                Select {
                    options: ["Fill", "Fit", "Stretch", "Center"];
                    current: layer.positioning == "Fit" ? "Fit"
                           : layer.positioning == "Stretch" ? "Stretch"
                           : layer.positioning == "Center" || layer.positioning == "Custom" ? "Center" : "Fill";
                    selected(v) => { root.positioning-changed(i, v); }
                }
            }
            if !layer.is-video : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 6px;
                Text { text: "BLEND MODE"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 8px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; }
                Select {
                    options: ["Normal", "Additive", "Screen", "Multiply"];
                    current: layer.blend-mode == "additive" ? "Additive"
                           : layer.blend-mode == "screen"   ? "Screen"
                           : layer.blend-mode == "multiply" ? "Multiply" : "Normal";
                    selected(v) => { root.blend-changed(i, v == "Additive" ? "additive"
                                                          : v == "Screen"   ? "screen"
                                                          : v == "Multiply" ? "multiply" : "normal"); }
                }
            }
            VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 6px;
                    Icon { name: "zap"; size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    Text { text: "OPACITY"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
                    Text { text: Math.round(layer.opacity * 100) + "%"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
                AccentSlider { minimum: 0; maximum: 100; value: layer.opacity * 100; changed(v) => { root.opacity-changed(i, v / 100); } }
            }
        }
    }
    if root.layers.length == 0 : Rectangle {
        height: 130px; border-radius: 16px;
        background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff06 : #00000005; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
        VerticalLayout {
            alignment: center; spacing: 8px;
            HorizontalLayout { alignment: center; Icon { name: "layers"; size: 28px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted.with-alpha(0.4); } }
            Text { text: "No layers on this display"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 12px; horizontal-alignment: center; }
            Text { text: "Assign a shader from the Library tab"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 11px; horizontal-alignment: center; }
        }
    }
}

component LayerStack inherits VerticalLayout {
    in property <[LayerItem]> layers;
    in property <string> monitor-name;
    // When true the list scrolls internally (wide side-panel); when false it just
    // stacks and the host page scrolls (narrow mode → a single scrollbar).
    in property <bool> scrollable: true;
    callback move-up(int);
    callback move-down(int);
    callback remove(int);
    callback opacity-changed(int, float);
    callback blend-changed(int, string);
    callback positioning-changed(int, string);
    callback visibility-toggled(int, bool);
    callback edit-requested(int);

    spacing: 16px;

    Rectangle {
        height: 60px; border-radius: 16px; background: Theme.palette.card; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
        HorizontalLayout {
            padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px; spacing: 12px;
            VerticalLayout { alignment: center; Icon { name: "layers"; size: 18px; color: Theme.palette.accent; } }
            VerticalLayout {
                horizontal-stretch: 1; alignment: center; spacing: 1px;
                Text { text: "LAYERS"; color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; }
                Text { text: root.monitor-name; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; overflow: elide; }
            }
            VerticalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    height: 22px; width: cnt.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px; background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.15);
                    cnt := Text { text: root.layers.length + " ITEMS"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800;
                           horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    if root.scrollable : ScrollView {
        vertical-stretch: 1;
        // Inline width-constrained wrapper (reserves the scrollbar gutter + lets the
        // ScrollView size the content) - same pattern the other tabs use.
        VerticalLayout {
            width: root.width - 26px;
            LayerList {
                layers: root.layers;
                move-up(i) => { root.move-up(i); }
                move-down(i) => { root.move-down(i); }
                remove(i) => { root.remove(i); }
                opacity-changed(i, o) => { root.opacity-changed(i, o); }
                blend-changed(i, b) => { root.blend-changed(i, b); }
                positioning-changed(i, p) => { root.positioning-changed(i, p); }
                visibility-toggled(i, v) => { root.visibility-toggled(i, v); }
                edit-requested(i) => { root.edit-requested(i); }
            }
        }
    }
    if !root.scrollable : LayerList {
        layers: root.layers;
        move-up(i) => { root.move-up(i); }
        move-down(i) => { root.move-down(i); }
        remove(i) => { root.remove(i); }
        opacity-changed(i, o) => { root.opacity-changed(i, o); }
        blend-changed(i, b) => { root.blend-changed(i, b); }
        positioning-changed(i, p) => { root.positioning-changed(i, p); }
        visibility-toggled(i, v) => { root.visibility-toggled(i, v); }
        edit-requested(i) => { root.edit-requested(i); }
    }
}

component WallpaperCard inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string>  name;
    in property <string>  author;
    in property <[string]> tags;
    in property <bool>    has-thumbnail;
    in property <image>   thumbnail;
    in property <[int]>   usage-counts;
    in property <[MonitorItem]> monitors;
    in property <bool>    is-active;
    in property <bool>    is-parallax;
    in property <bool>    is-imported;
    in property <bool>    is-video;
    in property <string>  source-url;
    callback toggle-monitor(int);
    callback delete-requested();
    callback open-url(string);

    // Use each monitor's actual color tag (set in the Compositor) so the Library
    // avatars / "Apply to" rows match the colors shown in the spatial canvas.
    pure function mon-color(idx: int) -> color {
        return MonColors.of(root.monitors[idx].color);
    }

    // Top corners SHARP so the full-bleed thumbnail sits flush; bottom corners rounded
    // to keep the card polished. (Software renderer can't round-clip the child image, so
    // matching the card's top edge to the image is the clean fix.)
    border-bottom-left-radius: 16px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 16px;
    background: Theme.palette.card;
    drop-shadow-blur: is-active ? 30px : (card-ta.has-hover ? 26px : 14px);
    drop-shadow-color: is-active ? Theme.palette.selection.with-alpha(0.30) : #00000038;
    drop-shadow-offset-y: 8px;
    clip: true;

    animate drop-shadow-blur, drop-shadow-color { duration: 300ms; easing: ease; }

    card-ta := TouchArea { mouse-cursor: default; }

    VerticalLayout {
        padding: 0; spacing: 0;

        // â"€â"€ Preview band (16:10) â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
        Rectangle {
            height: root.width * 10 / 16;
            // Full-bleed thumbnail with SHARP top corners - the card's top edge is sharp
            // too (only its bottom corners are rounded), so the square image fits flush.
            // This sidesteps the software renderer's inability to round-clip a child image.
            clip: true;
            background: Theme.is-dark ? #1a1d24 : #e4e8ef;

            if has-thumbnail : Image {
                source: root.thumbnail;
                width: 100%; height: 100%;
                image-fit: cover;
            }
            if !has-thumbnail : VerticalLayout {
                alignment: center; spacing: 8px;
                HorizontalLayout {
                    alignment: center;
                    Icon { name: "eye-off"; size: 30px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted.with-alpha(0.35); }
                }
                Text {
                    text: "NO PREVIEW";
                    color: Theme.palette.text-muted.with-alpha(0.6);
                    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 3px;
                    horizontal-alignment: center;
                }
            }
            Rectangle {
                y: parent.height - 48px; height: 48px; width: 100%;
                background: @linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, #000000aa 100%);
            }

            // Active pill (top-left)
            if is-active : Rectangle {
                x: 12px; y: 12px;
                height: 22px; width: active-row.preferred-width + 20px;
                border-radius: 11px;
                background: Theme.palette.selection;
                drop-shadow-blur: 12px; drop-shadow-color: Theme.palette.selection.with-alpha(0.4);
                active-row := HorizontalLayout {
                    padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; spacing: 4px; alignment: center;
                    Icon { name: "check"; size: 12px; color: #ffffff; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    Text { text: "ACTIVE"; color: #ffffff; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.5px; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }

            // Top-right: optional delete (parallax assets) + asset-type badge.
            HorizontalLayout {
                x: parent.width - self.preferred-width - 12px; y: 12px; spacing: 6px;

                // Delete - for user-generated cards: Parallax Studio creations and
                // imported Shadertoy shaders.
                if is-parallax || is-imported || is-video : Rectangle {
                    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 10px;
                    background: del-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.danger : #00000066;
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: #ffffff1a;
                    animate background { duration: 150ms; }
                    Icon { name: "trash-2"; size: 15px; color: #ffffff;
                           x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    del-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.delete-requested(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                }

                // Asset-type badge: blue sparkles for Parallax, the shader "zap"
                // otherwise - tinted RED when the shader was imported from Shadertoy.
                Rectangle {
                    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 10px;
                    background: is-video ? #ef444433 : (is-parallax ? #3b82f633 : (is-imported ? #ef444433 : #00000066));
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: is-video ? #ef4444aa : (is-parallax ? #3b82f6aa : (is-imported ? #ef4444aa : #ffffff1a));
                    Icon {
                        name: is-video ? "video" : (is-parallax ? "sparkles" : "zap"); size: 16px;
                        color: is-video ? #ef4444 : (is-parallax ? #3b82f6 : (is-imported ? #ef4444 : Theme.palette.selection));
                        x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // â"€â"€ Body â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
        VerticalLayout {
            padding: 18px; spacing: 14px;

            VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text {
                    text: root.name;
                    font-family: Theme.font-headline;
                    font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px;
                    color: Theme.palette.text;
                    overflow: elide;
                }
                // Attribution: "Made by <author>". When a source URL is known the
                // author is rendered as an accent-colored hyperlink that opens the
                // original page (satisfies Shadertoy's credit clause).
                if root.author != "" : HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 4px; alignment: start;
                    Text {
                        text: "Made by";
                        color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                        font-size: 12px;
                        vertical-alignment: center;
                    }
                    author-txt := Text {
                        text: root.author;
                        color: root.source-url != ""
                            ? (link-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.selection.brighter(0.2) : Theme.palette.selection)
                            : Theme.palette.text-muted;
                        font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
                        vertical-alignment: center;
                        overflow: elide;
                        link-ta := TouchArea {
                            enabled: root.source-url != "";
                            mouse-cursor: pointer;
                            clicked => { root.open-url(root.source-url); }
                        }
                    }
                }
                // Tag chips: rounded "#tag" pills (clipped to one row).
                // Always present at a fixed height so every card is the SAME
                // total height - otherwise the per-column stacks misalign into a
                // staircase instead of a neat grid.
                Rectangle {
                    height: 20px; clip: true;
                    HorizontalLayout {
                        spacing: 6px; alignment: start;
                        for tag in root.tags : Rectangle {
                            height: 20px; width: chip-txt.preferred-width + 16px;
                            border-radius: 6px;
                            background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff14 : #00000010;
                            chip-txt := Text {
                                text: "#" + tag;
                                color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                                font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
                                horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // Divider
            Rectangle { height: 1px; background: Theme.palette.border.with-alpha(0.5); }

            // Footer: applied-monitor avatars + Apply dropdown
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 8px; alignment: space-between;

                // Avatars of monitors this wallpaper is applied to
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: -6px; alignment: start;
                    for count[i] in root.usage-counts : Rectangle {
                        visible: count > 0;
                        width: count > 0 ? 28px : 0px; height: 28px; border-radius: 14px;
                        background: mon-color(i);
                        border-width: 2px; border-color: Theme.palette.card;
                        Text {
                            text: i + 1;
                            color: #ffffff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
                            horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center;
                        }
                    }
                }

                // Apply / Manage button → popup
                apply-btn := Rectangle {
                    height: 34px; width: btn-row.preferred-width + 24px;
                    border-radius: 9px;
                    background: btn-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.12) : transparent;
                    animate background { duration: 150ms; }
                    btn-row := HorizontalLayout {
                        padding-left: 12px; padding-right: 12px; spacing: 6px; alignment: center;
                        Text {
                            text: is-active ? "Manage Displays" : "Apply to";
                            color: btn-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text;
                            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px;
                            vertical-alignment: center;
                        }
                        Icon { name: "chevron-down"; size: 14px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                    }
                    btn-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { monitor-popup.show(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }

                    monitor-popup := PopupWindow {
                        x: apply-btn.width - 256px; y: apply-btn.height + 6px;
                        width: 256px;
                        Rectangle {
                            background: Theme.palette.card;
                            border-radius: 14px;
                            border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                            drop-shadow-blur: 30px; drop-shadow-color: #00000066;
                            VerticalLayout {
                                padding: 8px; spacing: 2px;
                                Text {
                                    text: "SELECT DISPLAY";
                                    color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 9px;
                                    font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px;
                                    horizontal-alignment: left;
                                    height: 24px; vertical-alignment: center;
                                }
                                for m[i] in root.monitors : Rectangle {
                                    height: 48px; border-radius: 9px;
                                    background: row-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.12) : transparent;
                                    row-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.toggle-monitor(i); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                                    HorizontalLayout {
                                        padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; spacing: 10px; alignment: start;
                                        Rectangle {
                                            width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px;
                                            background: mon-color(i);
                                            y: (parent.height - self.height)/2;
                                            Text { text: i+1; color: #ffffff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
                                                   horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                                        }
                                        VerticalLayout {
                                            alignment: center; horizontal-stretch: 1;
                                            Text { text: m.name; color: Theme.palette.text; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; overflow: elide; }
                                            Text { text: m.width + " x " + m.height; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; }
                                        }
                                        if root.usage-counts[i] > 0 : Icon {
                                            name: "check"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.selection;
                                            y: (parent.height - self.height)/2;
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // Active/selected outline - drawn LAST so it sits ON TOP of the thumbnail.
    // (The software renderer composites a child image over the parent's border,
    // unlike femtovg, so the border must be its own top-most overlay.) Matches the
    // card shape: sharp top, rounded bottom.
    Rectangle {
        border-bottom-left-radius: 16px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 16px;
        border-width: root.is-active ? 2px : 1px;
        border-color: root.is-active ? Theme.palette.selection : Theme.palette.border;
        background: transparent;
        animate border-color { duration: 300ms; easing: ease; }
    }
}

// ── Parallax Studio ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Ported from the ui-prototype ParallaxStudio. All controls are visual stubs
// (local state only) - backend depth/parallax wiring comes later.

// Slider row: label + live value badge + accent slider (local stub value).
component KineSlider inherits VerticalLayout {
    in property <string> label;
    in property <bool> muted: false;
    in property <float> minimum: 0;
    in property <float> maximum: 1;
    in-out property <float> value: 0;
    callback changed(float);
    spacing: 10px;
    HorizontalLayout {
        spacing: 8px;
        Text {
            text: root.label; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: root.muted ? Theme.palette.text-muted : Theme.palette.text;
            horizontal-stretch: 1; vertical-alignment: center;
        }
        Rectangle {
            height: 20px; width: kv.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
            background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
            kv := Text {
                text: Math.round(root.value * 100) / 100;
                color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;
                horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center;
            }
        }
    }
    AccentSlider {
        minimum: root.minimum; maximum: root.maximum; value: root.value;
        // NOTE: do NOT self-assign `root.value = v` here - that overwrites the
        // parent's `value: …` binding, so later external updates (e.g. the Reset
        // button setting params back to defaults) would no longer move the slider.
        // The owner updates `value` via the round-trip in `changed`, keeping the
        // binding intact so both drags and resets reflect.
        changed(v) => { root.changed(v); }
    }
}

// Pill button used for the Auto-detect and Render actions.
component PillButton inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> text;
    in property <string> icon;
    in property <length> btn-height: 48px;
    in property <bool> enabled: true;
    callback clicked();
    height: root.btn-height; border-radius: 14px;
    opacity: root.enabled ? 1.0 : 0.4;
    background: (root.enabled && pb-ta.has-hover) ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.2) : Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.2);
    animate background { duration: 150ms; }
    HorizontalLayout {
        alignment: center; spacing: 10px;
        Icon { name: root.icon; size: 18px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
        Text {
            text: root.text; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px; vertical-alignment: center;
        }
    }
    pb-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { if (root.enabled) { root.clicked(); } } mouse-cursor: root.enabled ? pointer : default; }
}

// Asset-pipeline + kinematics controls (the left column). Reused in both the
// wide (sidebar) and narrow (stacked) layouts.
component ParallaxControls inherits VerticalLayout {
    in-out property <string> mode: "automatic";
    in property <string> image-name;     // selected photo (empty = none yet)
    // Automatic mode: one Quality Preset bundles depth + matte + upscaler choices.
    in property <[string]> preset-options;
    in property <string> preset-current;
    in property <string> protip;          // automatic-mode guidance (from preset meta)
    // Manual mode: individual model dropdowns.
    in property <[string]> model-options;   // depth estimator
    in property <string> model-current;
    in property <[string]> seg-options;     // masking model
    in property <string> seg-current;
    in property <[string]> upscaler-options; // inpaint-detail upscaler
    in property <string> upscaler-current;
    // Parallax style (shown in both modes).
    in property <[string]> style-options;
    in property <string> style-current;
    // Unified model-download state (depth + matte + LaMa + upscaler for the selection).
    in property <bool>   models-need-download; // any required model missing
    in property <bool>   downloading;
    in property <string> download-text;        // e.g. "Depth Anything V2 Base · 195 MB (1/3)"
    in property <int>    download-percent;      // 0..100 of the current file
    // Manual-mode tuning knobs (baked into the shader; re-baked live on change).
    in property <float>  param-height;          // parallax strength
    in property <float>  param-zoom;            // zoom / edge cover
    in property <float>  param-steps;           // refinement quality
    callback open-image();
    callback auto-detect();
    callback preset-changed(string);
    callback model-changed(string);
    callback seg-changed(string);
    callback style-changed(string);
    callback upscaler-changed(string);
    callback download-models();
    callback param-changed(string, float);
    spacing: 24px;

    // Section 1 - Asset pipeline
    VerticalLayout {
        spacing: 14px;
        SectionLabel { icon: "layers"; text: "ASSET PIPELINE"; }
        SettingsPanel {
            // Upload dropzone (stub)
            Rectangle {
                height: 160px; border-radius: 16px;
                border-width: 2px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.25);
                background: dz-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.12) : Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.05);
                animate background { duration: 150ms; }
                VerticalLayout {
                    alignment: center; spacing: 12px;
                    HorizontalLayout {
                        alignment: center;
                        Rectangle {
                            width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 24px;
                            background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                            Icon { name: "upload"; size: 24px; color: Theme.palette.accent;
                                   x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                        }
                    }
                    Text { text: root.image-name == "" ? "Select an image" : root.image-name; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
                           color: Theme.palette.text; horizontal-alignment: center; overflow: elide; }
                    Text { text: root.image-name == "" ? "PNG, JPG OR WEBP" : "CLICK TO CHANGE"; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
                           color: Theme.palette.text-muted; horizontal-alignment: center; }
                }
                dz-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.open-image(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
            }
            // Settings mode (Automatic = preset-driven, foolproof; Manual = pick models)
            VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "SETTINGS"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select {
                    options: ["Automatic Mode", "Manual Mode"];
                    current: root.mode == "manual" ? "Manual Mode" : "Automatic Mode";
                    selected(v) => { root.mode = v == "Manual Mode" ? "manual" : "automatic"; }
                }
            }

            // ── AUTOMATIC - one Quality Preset bundles depth + matte + upscaler ──
            if root.mode == "automatic" : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "QUALITY PRESET"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select { options: root.preset-options; current: root.preset-current; selected(v) => { root.preset-changed(v); } }
            }
            if root.mode == "automatic" : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "PARALLAX STYLE"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select { options: root.style-options; current: root.style-current; selected(v) => { root.style-changed(v); } }
            }
            if root.mode == "automatic" && root.protip != "" : Rectangle {
                border-radius: 12px;
                background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.06);
                border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.18);
                HorizontalLayout {
                    padding: 12px; spacing: 10px;
                    Icon { name: "sparkles"; size: 14px; color: Theme.palette.accent; }
                    Text { text: root.protip; font-size: 11px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; wrap: word-wrap; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
                }
            }

            // ── MANUAL - individual model dropdowns ──
            if root.mode == "manual" : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "DEPTH ESTIMATOR MODEL"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select { options: root.model-options; current: root.model-current; selected(v) => { root.model-changed(v); } }
            }
            if root.mode == "manual" : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "MASKING MODEL"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select { options: root.seg-options; current: root.seg-current; selected(v) => { root.seg-changed(v); } }
            }
            if root.mode == "manual" : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "UPSCALER (INPAINT DETAIL)"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select { options: root.upscaler-options; current: root.upscaler-current; selected(v) => { root.upscaler-changed(v); } }
            }
            if root.mode == "manual" : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                Text { text: "PARALLAX STYLE"; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                Select { options: root.style-options; current: root.style-current; selected(v) => { root.style-changed(v); } }
            }

            // ── Unified model download (both modes) ──
            // Shown whenever the current selection needs models. One queued download with
            // a "(i/N)" + per-model name & size + live progress (see download-text/percent).
            if root.models-need-download || root.downloading : VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                if !root.downloading : Rectangle {
                    height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
                    background: dlq-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.2) : Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.25);
                    HorizontalLayout {
                        alignment: center; spacing: 8px;
                        Icon { name: "arrow-up-circle"; size: 15px; color: Theme.palette.accent; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                        Text { text: "DOWNLOAD REQUIRED MODELS"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
                               letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
                    }
                    dlq-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.download-models(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                }
                if root.downloading : VerticalLayout {
                    spacing: 6px;
                    Text { text: root.download-text; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; overflow: elide; }
                    Rectangle {
                        height: 6px; border-radius: 3px; background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff14 : #00000010;
                        Rectangle {
                            x: 0; y: 0; height: 100%;
                            width: parent.width * (root.download-percent / 100.0);
                            border-radius: 3px; background: Theme.palette.accent;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // Manual tuning - purpose-built knobs for our depth-parallax shader. They bake into
    // the wallpaper's shader; the sliders re-bake it LIVE (reusing the cached depth +
    // inpaint), so changes preview instantly without re-running the models.
    if root.mode == "manual" : VerticalLayout {
        spacing: 14px;
        HorizontalLayout {
            spacing: 8px;
            SectionLabel { icon: "settings-2"; text: "PARALLAX TUNING"; horizontal-stretch: 1; }
            // Reset all three tuning sliders to their defaults (matches the
            // Settings audio/mouse-sensitivity reset affordance).
            Rectangle {
                height: 22px; width: ptrst-txt.preferred-width + 16px; border-radius: 6px;
                background: ptrst-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : Theme.palette.card;
                border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;
                ptrst-txt := Text { text: "Reset"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;
                                    horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                ptrst-ta := TouchArea {
                    clicked => {
                        root.param-changed("height", 0.2);
                        root.param-changed("zoom", 1.06);
                        root.param-changed("steps", 10);
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        SettingsPanel {
            KineSlider {
                label: "PARALLAX STRENGTH"; minimum: 0.0; maximum: 0.30; value: root.param-height;
                changed(v) => { root.param-changed("height", v); }
            }
            KineSlider {
                label: "ZOOM (EDGE COVER)"; minimum: 1.0; maximum: 1.30; value: root.param-zoom;
                changed(v) => { root.param-changed("zoom", v); }
            }
            KineSlider {
                label: "QUALITY (STEPS)"; muted: true; minimum: 8.0; maximum: 64.0; value: root.param-steps;
                changed(v) => { root.param-changed("steps", v); }
            }
        }
    }
    if root.mode == "automatic" : SettingsPanel {
        VerticalLayout {
            alignment: center; spacing: 18px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 18px;
                    background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                    Icon { name: "cpu"; size: 32px; color: Theme.palette.accent;
                           x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                }
            }
            Text { text: "AUTOMATIC SETTINGS"; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px;
                   color: Theme.palette.text; horizontal-alignment: center; }
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    height: 20px; width: ad-up.preferred-width + 18px; border-radius: 6px;
                    background: Theme.palette.card-hover;
                    ad-up := Text { text: "UPCOMING"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800;
                                    letter-spacing: 2px; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
            Text {
                text: "Planned: detect your PC's hardware and pick the optimal quality preset automatically. Not available yet - choose a Quality Preset manually for now.";
                font-size: 11px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; horizontal-alignment: center; wrap: word-wrap;
            }
            // Disabled until spec-based auto-preset selection ships (see UPCOMING above).
            PillButton { text: "AUTO-DETECT"; icon: "sparkles"; enabled: false; clicked => { root.auto-detect(); } }
        }
    }
}

// Preview stage + timeline (the right column / bottom block).
component ParallaxPreview inherits VerticalLayout {
    in property <image> preview-image;   // live render; empty = show placeholder
    in property <string> status;         // shown in the timeline strip
    in property <int> progress;          // 0..100, drives the timeline bar
    spacing: 20px;

    // Previewer stage
    Rectangle {
        vertical-stretch: 1;
        border-radius: 32px; clip: true;
        background: Theme.is-dark ? #0a0d13 : #e6eaf1;
        border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;

        // Live preview render (fills the stage, preserving aspect).
        if root.preview-image.width > 0 : Image {
            source: root.preview-image;
            image-fit: contain;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
        }

        if root.preview-image.width == 0 : VerticalLayout {
            alignment: center; spacing: 22px; padding: 24px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    width: 96px; height: 96px; border-radius: 32px;
                    background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                    Icon { name: "video"; size: 48px; color: Theme.palette.accent;
                           x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                }
            }
            Text { text: "Kinematic Previewer"; font-family: Theme.font-headline; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;
                   color: Theme.palette.text; horizontal-alignment: center; }
            Text { text: "Select and upload an image, adjust settings and hit Render!";
                   font-size: 13px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; horizontal-alignment: center; wrap: word-wrap; }
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: center;
                Rectangle {
                    height: 28px; width: rdy-t.preferred-width + 28px; border-radius: 14px;
                    background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.08);
                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.2);
                    rdy-t := Text { text: "READY FOR INPUT"; color: Theme.palette.accent; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800;
                           letter-spacing: 2px; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                }
            }
        }

        // Top-left engine badge
        Rectangle {
            x: 24px; y: 24px; height: 24px; width: pe-t.preferred-width + 24px; border-radius: 12px;
            background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff12 : #00000010;
            border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff1a : #00000014;
            pe-t := Text { text: "PARALLAX ENGINE"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800;
                   letter-spacing: 3px; horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
        }
        // Top-right action buttons
        HorizontalLayout {
            x: parent.width - self.preferred-width - 24px; y: 24px; spacing: 10px;
            Rectangle {
                width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px;
                background: info-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : Theme.palette.card;
                border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                Icon { name: "info"; size: 18px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                info-ta := TouchArea { mouse-cursor: pointer; }
            }
            Rectangle {
                width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px;
                background: max-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : Theme.palette.card;
                border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                Icon { name: "maximize"; size: 18px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                max-ta := TouchArea { mouse-cursor: pointer; }
            }
        }
    }

    // Status / progress strip (was the "sequence timeline" placeholder).
    Rectangle {
        height: 96px; border-radius: 24px;
        background: Theme.palette.card; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
        VerticalLayout {
            padding: 24px; spacing: 16px;
            HorizontalLayout {
                property <bool> active: root.status != "";
                Text { text: parent.active ? root.status : "SEQUENCE TIMELINE";
                       font-size: parent.active ? 11px : 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: parent.active ? 0px : 2px;
                       color: parent.active ? Theme.palette.text : Theme.palette.text-muted; opacity: parent.active ? 1.0 : 0.6;
                       horizontal-stretch: 1; vertical-alignment: center; overflow: elide; }
                Text { text: parent.active ? (root.progress + "%") : "00:00:00 / 00:00:00";
                       font-size: parent.active ? 11px : 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: parent.active ? 0px : 2px;
                       color: parent.active ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text-muted; opacity: parent.active ? 1.0 : 0.6;
                       vertical-alignment: center; }
            }
            Rectangle {
                height: 6px; border-radius: 3px;
                background: Theme.is-dark ? #ffffff0d : #00000010;
                Rectangle {
                    x: 0; height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; background: Theme.palette.accent;
                    width: parent.width * (root.progress / 100.0);
                    animate width { duration: 200ms; easing: ease; }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

component ParallaxStudio inherits Rectangle {
    in-out property <string> mode: "automatic";
    // Side-by-side on wide windows; stacked + scrolling when narrow (like the
    // Compositor/Settings tabs) so nothing clips off the right on small windows.
    property <bool> wide: self.width >= 1000px;
    in property <string> image-name;   // selected photo file name (empty = none)
    in property <bool> busy;           // depth generation / export in progress
    in property <string> status;       // shown in the previewer's timeline strip
    in property <int> progress;        // 0..100 for the timeline bar
    in property <[string]> preset-options;
    in property <string> preset-current;
    in property <string> protip;
    in property <[string]> model-options;
    in property <string> model-current;
    in property <[string]> seg-options;
    in property <string> seg-current;
    in property <[string]> upscaler-options;
    in property <string> upscaler-current;
    in property <[string]> style-options;
    in property <string> style-current;
    in property <bool> models-need-download;
    in property <bool> downloading;
    in property <string> download-text;
    in property <int> download-percent;
    in property <float> param-height;
    in property <float> param-zoom;
    in property <float> param-steps;
    in property <image> preview-image;
    in property <bool> has-preview;
    callback open-image();
    callback auto-detect();
    callback render-requested();
    callback save-requested(string);   // the chosen library name ("" = use image file name)
    // Toggles the "name your wallpaper" dialog overlay (opened by SAVE TO LIBRARY).
    property <bool> show-name-dialog: false;
    callback preset-changed(string);
    callback model-changed(string);
    callback seg-changed(string);
    callback style-changed(string);
    callback upscaler-changed(string);
    callback download-models();
    callback param-changed(string, float);

    // Render button label + a status line, shared by both layouts.
    property <string> render-label: root.busy ? "WORKING…" : (root.has-preview ? "RE-RENDER" : "RENDER");

    // ── Wide: 400px control sidebar + stretching preview ──
    // (A layout auto-fills its Rectangle parent - no explicit 100% needed; an
    //  explicit 100% against the not-yet-sized parent can collapse to preferred.)
    if root.wide : HorizontalLayout {
        spacing: 24px;
        Rectangle {
            // Sidebar widened so the cards keep their full width AND there's a
            // 34px scrollbar gutter (422 − 388), matching the Compositor's inset -
            // the preview just takes the remaining width. The render/save buttons
            // span the full sidebar (full-width actions, by design).
            width: 422px;
            VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 16px;
                ScrollView {
                    vertical-stretch: 1;
                    // Wrap in a fixed-width VerticalLayout so the ScrollView sizes
                    // the content by its PREFERRED height (and thus scrolls when the
                    // pipeline + tuning cards overflow a short/scaled window) instead
                    // of stretching the controls to fit and clipping the last card.
                    // The width also reserves the scrollbar gutter (same pattern as
                    // the narrow layout + Compositor) so the highlighted scrollbar
                    // never collides with the card edges.
                    VerticalLayout {
                        width: 388px;
                        ParallaxControls {
                        mode <=> root.mode;
                        image-name: root.image-name;
                        preset-options: root.preset-options;
                        preset-current: root.preset-current;
                        protip: root.protip;
                        model-options: root.model-options;
                        model-current: root.model-current;
                        seg-options: root.seg-options;
                        seg-current: root.seg-current;
                        upscaler-options: root.upscaler-options;
                        upscaler-current: root.upscaler-current;
                        style-options: root.style-options;
                        style-current: root.style-current;
                        models-need-download: root.models-need-download;
                        downloading: root.downloading;
                        download-text: root.download-text;
                        download-percent: root.download-percent;
                        param-height: root.param-height;
                        param-zoom: root.param-zoom;
                        param-steps: root.param-steps;
                        open-image => { root.open-image(); }
                        auto-detect => { root.auto-detect(); }
                        preset-changed(v) => { root.preset-changed(v); }
                        model-changed(v) => { root.model-changed(v); }
                        seg-changed(v) => { root.seg-changed(v); }
                        style-changed(v) => { root.style-changed(v); }
                        upscaler-changed(v) => { root.upscaler-changed(v); }
                        download-models => { root.download-models(); }
                        param-changed(n, v) => { root.param-changed(n, v); }
                        }
                    }
                }
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 10px;
                    PillButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; btn-height: 56px; text: root.render-label; icon: "video"; clicked => { if (!root.busy) { root.render-requested(); } } }
                    PillButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; btn-height: 56px; text: "SAVE TO LIBRARY"; icon: "save"; enabled: root.has-preview && !root.busy; clicked => { root.show-name-dialog = true; } }
                }
            }
        }
        ParallaxPreview { horizontal-stretch: 1; preview-image: root.preview-image; status: root.status; progress: root.progress; }
    }

    // ── Narrow: single scrolling column (controls → render → preview) ──
    if !root.wide : ScrollView {
        VerticalLayout {
            width: root.width - 26px;
            padding: 4px; spacing: 24px;
            ParallaxControls {
                mode <=> root.mode;
                image-name: root.image-name;
                preset-options: root.preset-options;
                preset-current: root.preset-current;
                protip: root.protip;
                model-options: root.model-options;
                model-current: root.model-current;
                seg-options: root.seg-options;
                seg-current: root.seg-current;
                upscaler-options: root.upscaler-options;
                upscaler-current: root.upscaler-current;
                style-options: root.style-options;
                style-current: root.style-current;
                models-need-download: root.models-need-download;
                downloading: root.downloading;
                download-text: root.download-text;
                download-percent: root.download-percent;
                param-height: root.param-height;
                param-zoom: root.param-zoom;
                param-steps: root.param-steps;
                open-image => { root.open-image(); }
                auto-detect => { root.auto-detect(); }
                preset-changed(v) => { root.preset-changed(v); }
                model-changed(v) => { root.model-changed(v); }
                seg-changed(v) => { root.seg-changed(v); }
                style-changed(v) => { root.style-changed(v); }
                upscaler-changed(v) => { root.upscaler-changed(v); }
                download-models => { root.download-models(); }
                param-changed(n, v) => { root.param-changed(n, v); }
            }
            HorizontalLayout {
                spacing: 10px;
                PillButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; btn-height: 56px; text: root.render-label; icon: "video"; clicked => { if (!root.busy) { root.render-requested(); } } }
                PillButton { horizontal-stretch: 1; btn-height: 56px; text: "SAVE TO LIBRARY"; icon: "save"; enabled: root.has-preview && !root.busy; clicked => { root.show-name-dialog = true; } }
            }
            ParallaxPreview { height: 460px; preview-image: root.preview-image; status: root.status; progress: root.progress; }
        }
    }

    // ── "Name your wallpaper" dialog (opened by SAVE TO LIBRARY) ──────────────
    if root.show-name-dialog : Rectangle {
        // Dim full-cover backdrop; clicking it cancels.
        background: #000000aa;
        TouchArea { clicked => { root.show-name-dialog = false; } }
        Rectangle {
            width: 400px; height: name-col.preferred-height + 48px;
            x: (parent.width - self.width) / 2;
            y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;
            background: Theme.palette.card;
            border-radius: 16px; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
            drop-shadow-blur: 40px; drop-shadow-color: #00000066;
            // Absorb clicks so they don't fall through to the dismissing backdrop.
            TouchArea {}
            name-col := VerticalLayout {
                padding: 24px; spacing: 14px;
                Text { text: "Name your wallpaper"; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "Optional - leave blank to use the image's file name."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; wrap: word-wrap; }
                name-input := BlueInput { placeholder: "My Parallax Wallpaper"; }
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 12px; alignment: end;
                    Rectangle {
                        width: 96px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px;
                        background: cancel-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
                        border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                        Text { text: "CANCEL"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px;
                               horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                        cancel-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.show-name-dialog = false; } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                    }
                    PillButton {
                        width: 140px; btn-height: 44px; text: "SAVE"; icon: "save";
                        clicked => {
                            root.save-requested(name-input.text);
                            root.show-name-dialog = false;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

// â"€â"€ Wallpaper render window (borderless, no decorations) â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

export component WallpaperWindow inherits Window {
    background: black;
    no-frame: true;
}

// â"€â"€ Main app window â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€

// Bottom-right transient notification (matches the ui-prototype toaster). The
// stack is driven by the `toasts` model; auto-dismiss timing is owned by Rust.
component ToastCard inherits Rectangle {
    in property <string> title;
    in property <string> description;
    in property <bool> destructive;
    callback dismissed();

    width: 360px;
    height: layout.preferred-height;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: root.destructive ? Theme.palette.danger.with-alpha(0.12) : Theme.palette.card;
    border-width: 1px;
    border-color: root.destructive ? Theme.palette.danger.with-alpha(0.55) : Theme.palette.border;
    drop-shadow-color: #00000055;
    drop-shadow-blur: 18px;
    drop-shadow-offset-y: 6px;
    // Subtle entrance fade (the y is owned by the stack layout, so we can't
    // animate position here - opacity alone reads cleanly).
    opacity: 0;
    init => { self.opacity = 1; }
    animate opacity { duration: 180ms; easing: ease-out; }

    layout := HorizontalLayout {
        padding: 16px;
        spacing: 12px;
        VerticalLayout {
            horizontal-stretch: 1;
            spacing: 3px;
            alignment: center;
            Text {
                text: root.title;
                font-family: Theme.font-headline;
                font-size: 13px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: root.destructive ? Theme.palette.danger : Theme.palette.text;
                wrap: word-wrap;
            }
            if root.description != "" : Text {
                text: root.description;
                font-size: 11px;
                color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                wrap: word-wrap;
            }
        }
        VerticalLayout {
            alignment: start;
            Rectangle {
                width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 4px;
                background: close-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
                Icon { name: "x"; size: 12px;
                       color: close-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.text : Theme.palette.text-muted;
                       x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                close-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.dismissed(); } }
            }
        }
    }
}

export component AppWindow inherits Window {
    title: "Strata - Live Wallpaper Engine";
    min-width: 960px; min-height: 680px;
    background: Theme.palette.background;
    default-font-family: Theme.font-body;
    icon: @image-url("../../../assets/app-icon_dark.png");

    // Keep the std-widgets palette (used by ScrollView scrollbars) in sync with
    // our custom theme, so scrollbars are visible/correct in both light & dark.
    // (Palette accent colors are read-only here, so std widgets we want fully
    // themed - e.g. the name-input field - are custom components instead.)
    property <bool> is-dark-tracker: Theme.is-dark;
    init => { Palette.color-scheme = Theme.is-dark ? ColorScheme.dark : ColorScheme.light; }
    changed is-dark-tracker => { Palette.color-scheme = self.is-dark-tracker ? ColorScheme.dark : ColorScheme.light; }

    // â"€â"€ Data bindings â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
    in property <float> fps: 0;
    in property <float> frame-time: 0;
    in property <float> vram-usage: 0;
    // True when at least one shader layer is being rendered. When false the
    // telemetry cards show an "Inactive" state instead of an alarming 0 FPS / LOW.
    in property <bool> engine-active: false;
    in property <[LogEntry]> logs: [];

    in property <[WallpaperItem]> wallpapers: [];
    in property <[MonitorItem]>   monitors: [];
    in property <[LayerItem]>     layers: [];
    in property <[ToastData]>     toasts: [];
    // Default to the first display so the Compositor always opens with a monitor
    // selected (and editable) instead of requiring the user to click one first.
    in property <int> selected-monitor-index: 0;
    // Compositor spatial edit-mode draft (monitor pixels).
    in-out property <int>   editing-layer: -1;
    in-out property <float> edit-x;
    in-out property <float> edit-y;
    in-out property <float> edit-w;
    in-out property <float> edit-h;

    in property <int> canvas-min-x: 0;
    in property <int> canvas-min-y: 0;
    in property <int> canvas-max-x: 1920;
    in property <int> canvas-max-y: 1080;

    in-out property <bool> span-monitors:  false;
    in-out property <bool> debug-overlay:  false;
    in-out property <bool> autostart:      false;
    in-out property <bool> disable-mpo:    false;
    in-out property <int>  fps-cap:        60;
    in-out property <string> vsync-mode:     "Fifo (VSync On)";
    in-out property <string> shader-quality: "High (Maximum Fidelity)";
    in-out property <float>  audio-sensitivity: 1.0;
    in-out property <string> mouse-mode: "On (Only Parallax Studio)";
    in-out property <float>  mouse-sensitivity: 1.0;
    in-out property <string> search-query: "";
    // Library thumbnail refresh: `refreshing` is true while the background thumb
    // generator runs (accents the refresh icon; the toast signals progress).
    in-out property <bool>   refreshing: false;

    // Private state
    in-out property <string> active-tab: "library";

    // â"€â"€ Callbacks â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
    callback theme-changed(string);
    callback quit-requested();
    callback import-requested();
    // Movie-wallpaper import naming dialog (parallel to the parallax save dialog).
    in-out property <bool>   show-video-name-dialog: false;
    in-out property <string> video-name-default: "";
    callback video-import-confirmed(string); // the chosen name ("" = use file name)
    callback refresh-library();
    callback wallpaper-delete-requested(int);
    // Open an external URL (e.g. a shader's original Shadertoy page) in the browser.
    callback open-url(string);
    // Updates: GitHub-release check. Rust sets the badge/label/flags; the button
    // either runs the check or (when an update is available) opens the releases page.
    in-out property <string> update-version-badge: "v1.1.0 (LATEST)";
    in-out property <string> update-button-label: "CHECK FOR UPDATES";
    in-out property <string> update-url;          // latest release page (when available)
    in-out property <bool> update-available;
    in-out property <bool> update-checking;
    callback check-for-updates();
    // Asset Library (Strata-Library) update state - mirrors the engine's.
    in-out property <string> lib-update-version-badge: "v1.1.0 (LATEST)";
    in-out property <string> lib-update-button-label: "CHECK FOR UPDATES";
    in-out property <string> lib-update-url;
    in-out property <bool> lib-update-available;
    in-out property <bool> lib-update-checking;
    callback check-for-library-updates();
    // Parallax Studio
    callback parallax-pick-image();
    callback parallax-create();
    callback parallax-save(string);
    callback parallax-preset-changed(string);
    callback parallax-model-changed(string);
    callback parallax-seg-changed(string);
    callback parallax-style-changed(string);
    callback parallax-upscaler-changed(string);
    callback parallax-download-models();
    in-out property <string> parallax-mode: "automatic";
    in-out property <[string]> parallax-preset-options: [];
    in-out property <string> parallax-preset-current: "";
    in-out property <string> parallax-protip: "";
    in-out property <[string]> parallax-seg-options: [];
    in-out property <string> parallax-seg-current: "";
    in-out property <[string]> parallax-style-options: [];
    in-out property <string> parallax-style-current: "";
    in-out property <[string]> parallax-upscaler-options: [];
    in-out property <string> parallax-upscaler-current: "";
    in-out property <string> parallax-image-name: "";
    in-out property <bool>   parallax-busy: false;
    in-out property <string> parallax-status: "";
    in-out property <int>    parallax-progress: 0;
    in-out property <image>  parallax-preview-image;
    in-out property <bool>   parallax-has-preview: false;
    in-out property <[string]> parallax-model-options: ["Fast (no model)"];
    in-out property <string> parallax-model-current: "Fast (no model)";
    in-out property <bool>   parallax-models-need-download: false;
    in-out property <string> parallax-download-text: "";
    in-out property <int>    parallax-download-percent: 0;
    in-out property <bool>   parallax-downloading: false;
    in-out property <float>  parallax-param-height: 0.2;
    in-out property <float>  parallax-param-zoom: 1.06;
    in-out property <float>  parallax-param-steps: 10;
    callback parallax-param-changed(string, float);
    callback search-edited(string);
    callback monitor-selected(int);
    callback layer-opacity-changed(int, float);
    callback layer-remove-requested(int);
    callback apply-to-monitor(int, string);
    callback layer-positioning-changed(int, string);
    callback layer-scale-changed(int, float);
    callback layer-move-up(int);
    callback layer-move-down(int);
    callback layer-transform-changed(int, float, float, float, float);
    callback layer-transform-live(int, float, float, float, float); // live drag preview (no save)
    callback layer-edit-cancelled(); // discard → revert the live preview
    callback layer-visibility-toggled(int, bool);
    callback layer-blend-changed(int, string);
    callback monitor-rename(int, string);
    callback monitor-color-changed(int, string);
    callback span-toggled(bool);
    callback debug-toggled(bool);
    callback autostart-toggled(bool);
    callback mpo-toggled(bool);
    callback vsync-changed(string);
    callback fps-cap-changed(int);
    callback shader-quality-changed(string);
    callback copy-logs();
    callback open-debugger();
    callback refresh-monitors();
    callback toast-dismissed(int);
    callback audio-sensitivity-changed(float);
    callback mouse-mode-changed(string);
    callback mouse-sensitivity-changed(float);

    // â"€â"€ Root layout â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
    HorizontalLayout {
        padding: 0; spacing: 0;

        // â"€â"€ Sidebar â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
        Rectangle {
            width: 256px;
            background: Theme.palette.sidebar;
            // Right hairline border
            Rectangle { x: parent.width - 1px; width: 1px; height: 100%; background: Theme.palette.border; }

            VerticalLayout {
                padding: 24px; spacing: 8px;

                // â"€â"€ Logo + wordmark â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
                HorizontalLayout {
                    padding-bottom: 32px; spacing: 12px; alignment: start;
                    AppLogo { width: 40px; height: 40px; is-dark: Theme.is-dark; }
                    VerticalLayout {
                        alignment: center; spacing: 3px;
                        Text {
                            text: L10n.app-name;
                            font-family: Theme.font-headline;
                            font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;
                            color: Theme.palette.text;
                        }
                        Text {
                            text: L10n.app-tagline;
                            font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
                            color: Theme.palette.accent;
                        }
                    }
                }

                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "library"; text: L10n.tab-library;
                    active: root.active-tab == "library";
                    clicked => { root.active-tab = "library"; }
                }
                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "layers"; text: L10n.tab-compositor;
                    active: root.active-tab == "compositor";
                    clicked => { root.active-tab = "compositor"; }
                }
                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "sparkles"; text: L10n.tab-parallax;
                    active: root.active-tab == "parallax";
                    clicked => { root.active-tab = "parallax"; }
                }
                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "activity"; text: L10n.tab-diagnostics;
                    active: root.active-tab == "diagnostics";
                    clicked => { root.active-tab = "diagnostics"; }
                }
                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "settings-2"; text: L10n.tab-settings;
                    active: root.active-tab == "settings";
                    clicked => { root.active-tab = "settings"; }
                }

                Rectangle { vertical-stretch: 1; }

                Rectangle { height: 1px; background: Theme.palette.border; }
                Rectangle { height: 8px; }

                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "discord"; text: "Discord Server";
                    clicked => { root.open-url("https://discord.gg/qRdVSkUW6n"); }
                }
                SidebarButton {
                    icon: "log-out"; text: L10n.btn-quit; danger: true;
                    clicked => { root.quit-requested(); }
                }
            }
        }

        // â"€â"€ Main content area â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
        VerticalLayout {
            padding: 32px; spacing: 24px;

            // â"€â"€ Header: editorial title + subtitle â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
            VerticalLayout {
                spacing: 8px;
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 14px; alignment: start;
                    Text {
                        text: root.active-tab == "library"     ? L10n.title-library
                            : root.active-tab == "compositor"  ? L10n.title-compositor
                            : root.active-tab == "parallax"    ? L10n.title-parallax
                            : root.active-tab == "diagnostics" ? L10n.title-diagnostics
                            : L10n.title-settings;
                        font-family: Theme.font-headline;
                        font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700;
                        color: Theme.palette.text;
                        vertical-alignment: center;
                    }
                }
                Text {
                    text: root.active-tab == "library"     ? L10n.sub-library
                        : root.active-tab == "compositor"  ? L10n.sub-compositor
                        : root.active-tab == "parallax"    ? L10n.sub-parallax
                        : root.active-tab == "diagnostics" ? L10n.sub-diagnostics
                        : L10n.sub-settings;
                    color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 14px;
                }
            }

            // == Library tab ===================================================
            if root.active-tab == "library" : VerticalLayout {
                vertical-stretch: 1; spacing: 24px;

                // â"€â"€ Toolbar: search + refresh + import â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 12px;

                    // Search field (icon + inline editor with placeholder)
                    Rectangle {
                        horizontal-stretch: 1; height: 48px;
                        border-radius: 12px;
                        clip: true;
                        background: Theme.palette.card;
                        border-width: 1px;
                        border-color: search-input.has-focus ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.border;
                        animate border-color { duration: 150ms; }
                        HorizontalLayout {
                            padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 14px; spacing: 10px;
                            VerticalLayout {
                                alignment: center;
                                Icon { name: "search"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                            }
                            Rectangle {
                                horizontal-stretch: 1;
                                clip: true;
                                search-input := TextInput {
                                    width: 100%; height: 100%;
                                    vertical-alignment: center;
                                    single-line: true;
                                    color: Theme.palette.text;
                                    font-size: 14px;
                                    text: root.search-query;
                                    edited => { root.search-query = self.text; root.search-edited(self.text); }
                                }
                                if root.search-query == "" : Text {
                                    width: 100%; height: 100%;
                                    vertical-alignment: center;
                                    text: L10n.search-placeholder;
                                    color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                                    font-size: 14px;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }

                    // Refresh library
                    Rectangle {
                        width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
                        background: rf-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : Theme.palette.card;
                        border-width: 1px;
                        border-color: rf-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.border;
                        animate border-color, background { duration: 150ms; }
                        // Accented while a refresh is generating thumbnails; the
                        // toast notification already signals progress, so no spin.
                        Icon {
                            name: "refresh-cw";
                            size: 18px;
                            color: root.refreshing ? Theme.palette.accent : Theme.palette.text-muted;
                            x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2;
                        }
                        rf-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.refresh-library(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                    }

                    // Import (primary CTA)
                    Rectangle {
                        height: 48px; width: imp-row.preferred-width + 40px; border-radius: 12px;
                        background: imp-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.accent.brighter(0.12) : Theme.palette.accent;
                        drop-shadow-blur: 16px; drop-shadow-color: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.3); drop-shadow-offset-y: 4px;
                        animate background { duration: 150ms; }
                        imp-row := HorizontalLayout {
                            padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; spacing: 8px; alignment: center;
                            Icon { name: "plus"; size: 16px; color: #ffffff; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                            Text { text: L10n.btn-import; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800;
                                   letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-alignment: center; }
                        }
                        imp-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.import-requested(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                    }
                }

                // â"€â"€ Responsive card grid â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€â"€
                // Column count follows the prototype's Tailwind breakpoints
                // (1 / sm:2 / lg:3 / xl:4) on the window width.  Each column is a
                // stretching lane; card i lives in column (i mod cols), row (i div
                // cols) â€" i.e. row-major fill identical to a CSS grid.  Only the
                // active lanes exist (no phantom-spacing from empty wrappers).
                grid-area := Rectangle {
                    vertical-stretch: 1;
                    property <int> cols: root.width < 640px ? 1
                                       : root.width < 1024px ? 2
                                       : root.width < 1280px ? 3 : 4;
                    // Exactly `cols` lane indices so the row has no phantom empty
                    // columns (Slint has no range literal, so enumerate cases).
                    property <[float]> lanes: root.width < 640px ? [0]
                                            : root.width < 1024px ? [0, 1]
                                            : root.width < 1280px ? [0, 1, 2] : [0, 1, 2, 3];
                    // Explicit, identical column width so every card is the same
                    // size regardless of content. Reserve a right gutter (34px =
                    // 8px padding + scrollbar lane + a few px breathing room) so the
                    // hover-expanded vertical scrollbar never touches the card
                    // borders; then split the rest into equal columns minus gaps.
                    property <length> col-width: (self.width - 34px - (cols - 1) * 32px) / cols;
                    ScrollView {
                        VerticalLayout {
                            // Constrain content to the viewport width (minus the
                            // scrollbar gutter) so columns share exactly the
                            // available space - never overflow into a horizontal
                            // scrollbar / clipped cards at small window sizes.
                            width: grid-area.width - 26px;
                            padding: 4px;
                            if root.wallpapers.length > 0 : HorizontalLayout {
                                spacing: 32px; alignment: start;
                                for lane in grid-area.lanes : VerticalLayout {
                                    width: grid-area.col-width;
                                    spacing: 0; alignment: start;
                                    // One wrapper per wallpaper (always present); the
                                    // 32px gap lives in per-card bottom padding so
                                    // non-matching iterations contribute zero height.
                                    for wallpaper[i] in root.wallpapers : VerticalLayout {
                                        padding-bottom: (wallpaper.visible && Math.mod(i, grid-area.cols) == lane) ? 32px : 0px;
                                        if wallpaper.visible && (Math.mod(i, grid-area.cols) == lane) : WallpaperCard {
                                            name:          wallpaper.name;
                                            author:        wallpaper.author;
                                            tags:          wallpaper.tags;
                                            has-thumbnail: wallpaper.has-thumbnail;
                                            thumbnail:     wallpaper.thumbnail;
                                            usage-counts:  wallpaper.usage-counts;
                                            monitors:      root.monitors;
                                            is-active:     wallpaper.is-active;
                                            is-parallax:   wallpaper.is-parallax;
                                            is-imported:   wallpaper.is-imported;
                                            is-video:      wallpaper.is-video;
                                            source-url:    wallpaper.source-url;
                                            open-url(u) => { root.open-url(u); }
                                            toggle-monitor(idx) => { root.apply-to-monitor(idx, wallpaper.name); }
                                            delete-requested => { root.wallpaper-delete-requested(i); }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            if root.wallpapers.length == 0 : VerticalLayout {
                                alignment: center; spacing: 14px;
                                HorizontalLayout {
                                    alignment: center;
                                    Icon { name: "library"; size: 40px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted.with-alpha(0.4); }
                                }
                                Text {
                                    text: L10n.no-wallpapers;
                                    color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                                    horizontal-alignment: center; font-size: 14px;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // == Parallax Studio ===============================================
            if root.active-tab == "parallax" : ParallaxStudio {
                vertical-stretch: 1;
                mode <=> root.parallax-mode;
                image-name: root.parallax-image-name;
                busy: root.parallax-busy;
                status: root.parallax-status;
                preset-options: root.parallax-preset-options;
                preset-current: root.parallax-preset-current;
                protip: root.parallax-protip;
                model-options: root.parallax-model-options;
                model-current: root.parallax-model-current;
                seg-options: root.parallax-seg-options;
                seg-current: root.parallax-seg-current;
                style-options: root.parallax-style-options;
                style-current: root.parallax-style-current;
                upscaler-options: root.parallax-upscaler-options;
                upscaler-current: root.parallax-upscaler-current;
                models-need-download: root.parallax-models-need-download;
                downloading: root.parallax-downloading;
                download-text: root.parallax-download-text;
                download-percent: root.parallax-download-percent;
                param-height: root.parallax-param-height;
                param-zoom: root.parallax-param-zoom;
                param-steps: root.parallax-param-steps;
                preview-image: root.parallax-preview-image;
                has-preview: root.parallax-has-preview;
                progress: root.parallax-progress;
                open-image => { root.parallax-pick-image(); }
                render-requested => { root.parallax-create(); }
                auto-detect => { root.parallax-create(); }
                save-requested(n) => { root.parallax-save(n); }
                preset-changed(v) => { root.parallax-preset-changed(v); }
                model-changed(v) => { root.parallax-model-changed(v); }
                seg-changed(v) => { root.parallax-seg-changed(v); }
                style-changed(v) => { root.parallax-style-changed(v); }
                upscaler-changed(v) => { root.parallax-upscaler-changed(v); }
                download-models => { root.parallax-download-models(); }
                param-changed(n, v) => { root.parallax-param-changed(n, v); }
            }

            // â•گâ•گ Compositor tab â•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گ
            // == Compositor tab ===============================================
            // Spatial canvas + layer stack; side-by-side on wide windows, stacked
            // when narrow (canvas on top, layers below).
            if root.active-tab == "compositor" : comp-area := Rectangle {
                vertical-stretch: 1;
                property <bool> wide: root.width >= 1100px;

                if comp-area.wide : HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 24px;
                    CompositorCanvas {
                        horizontal-stretch: 1;
                        monitors: root.monitors; selected-index: root.selected-monitor-index; span: root.span-monitors;
                        canvas-min-x: root.canvas-min-x; canvas-min-y: root.canvas-min-y;
                        canvas-max-x: root.canvas-max-x; canvas-max-y: root.canvas-max-y;
                        editing-layer <=> root.editing-layer;
                        edit-x <=> root.edit-x; edit-y <=> root.edit-y; edit-w <=> root.edit-w; edit-h <=> root.edit-h;
                        monitor-selected(i) => { root.monitor-selected(i); }
                        refresh => { root.refresh-monitors(); }
                        span-toggled(v) => { root.span-monitors = v; root.span-toggled(v); }
                        rename(i, n) => { root.monitor-rename(i, n); }
                        color-changed(i, c) => { root.monitor-color-changed(i, c); }
                        edit-save => { root.layer-transform-changed(root.editing-layer, root.edit-x, root.edit-y, root.edit-w, root.edit-h); root.editing-layer = -1; }
                        edit-cancel => { root.editing-layer = -1; root.layer-edit-cancelled(); }
                        edit-live => { root.layer-transform-live(root.editing-layer, root.edit-x, root.edit-y, root.edit-w, root.edit-h); }
                    }
                    LayerStack {
                        width: 360px;
                        layers: root.layers;
                        monitor-name: root.selected-monitor-index >= 0 ? root.monitors[root.selected-monitor-index].name : "No display selected";
                        move-up(i) => { root.layer-move-up(i); }
                        move-down(i) => { root.layer-move-down(i); }
                        remove(i) => { root.layer-remove-requested(i); }
                        opacity-changed(i, o) => { root.layer-opacity-changed(i, o); }
                        blend-changed(i, b) => { root.layer-blend-changed(i, b); }
                        positioning-changed(i, p) => { root.layer-positioning-changed(i, p); }
                        visibility-toggled(i, v) => { root.layer-visibility-toggled(i, v); }
                        edit-requested(i) => {
                            root.editing-layer = i;
                            root.edit-x = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].x : 0;
                            root.edit-y = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].y : 0;
                            root.edit-w = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].width  : root.monitors[root.selected-monitor-index].width;
                            root.edit-h = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].height : root.monitors[root.selected-monitor-index].height;
                        }
                    }
                }

                // Narrow: canvas on top (fixed height), layer panel scrolling below.
                // The canvas must stay OUTSIDE the ScrollView - a Flickable captures
                // pointer drags, which would steal the edit-overlay's move/resize
                // gestures (the bug that made editing only work in the wide layout).
                if !comp-area.wide : VerticalLayout {
                    padding: 4px; spacing: 24px;
                    CompositorCanvas {
                        height: 300px;
                        monitors: root.monitors; selected-index: root.selected-monitor-index; span: root.span-monitors;
                        canvas-min-x: root.canvas-min-x; canvas-min-y: root.canvas-min-y;
                        canvas-max-x: root.canvas-max-x; canvas-max-y: root.canvas-max-y;
                        editing-layer <=> root.editing-layer;
                        edit-x <=> root.edit-x; edit-y <=> root.edit-y; edit-w <=> root.edit-w; edit-h <=> root.edit-h;
                        monitor-selected(i) => { root.monitor-selected(i); }
                        refresh => { root.refresh-monitors(); }
                        span-toggled(v) => { root.span-monitors = v; root.span-toggled(v); }
                        rename(i, n) => { root.monitor-rename(i, n); }
                        color-changed(i, c) => { root.monitor-color-changed(i, c); }
                        edit-save => { root.layer-transform-changed(root.editing-layer, root.edit-x, root.edit-y, root.edit-w, root.edit-h); root.editing-layer = -1; }
                        edit-cancel => { root.editing-layer = -1; root.layer-edit-cancelled(); }
                        edit-live => { root.layer-transform-live(root.editing-layer, root.edit-x, root.edit-y, root.edit-w, root.edit-h); }
                    }
                    ScrollView {
                        vertical-stretch: 1;
                        // Match the working tabs: an INLINE width-constrained VerticalLayout
                        // is what reserves the scrollbar gutter and lets the ScrollView size
                        // the content (setting width on the LayerStack component directly does
                        // not constrain it inside a ScrollView, so the cards ran full-width
                        // over where the scrollbar should be).
                        VerticalLayout {
                            // -34px (not -26) because this ScrollView sits inside the 4px-
                            // padded canvas/list column, so we reserve a touch more to keep
                            // the SAME visible gap between the cards and the scrollbar lane
                            // that the other tabs have (no hover collision with card edges).
                            width: comp-area.width - 34px;
                            padding: 4px;
                            LayerStack {
                                // No inner scroll - this ScrollView handles it.
                                scrollable: false;
                                layers: root.layers;
                                monitor-name: root.selected-monitor-index >= 0 ? root.monitors[root.selected-monitor-index].name : "No display selected";
                                move-up(i) => { root.layer-move-up(i); }
                                move-down(i) => { root.layer-move-down(i); }
                                remove(i) => { root.layer-remove-requested(i); }
                                opacity-changed(i, o) => { root.layer-opacity-changed(i, o); }
                                blend-changed(i, b) => { root.layer-blend-changed(i, b); }
                                visibility-toggled(i, v) => { root.layer-visibility-toggled(i, v); }
                                edit-requested(i) => {
                                    root.editing-layer = i;
                                    root.edit-x = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].x : 0;
                                    root.edit-y = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].y : 0;
                                    root.edit-w = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].width  : root.monitors[root.selected-monitor-index].width;
                                    root.edit-h = root.layers[i].positioning == "Custom" ? root.layers[i].height : root.monitors[root.selected-monitor-index].height;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // â•گâ•گ Settings tab â•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گ
            // â•گâ•گ Settings tab â•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گ
            // Two-column on wide windows, single stacked column when narrow so the
            // panels always fill the width and never clip out of the window.
            if root.active-tab == "settings" : settings-area := Rectangle {
                vertical-stretch: 1;
                property <bool> two-col: root.width >= 1080px;
                ScrollView {
                    VerticalLayout {
                        width: settings-area.width - 26px;
                        padding: 4px;

                        // â”€â”€ Wide: two columns (7 / 5) â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
                        if settings-area.two-col : HorizontalLayout {
                            spacing: 32px; alignment: stretch;
                            VerticalLayout {
                                horizontal-stretch: 7; spacing: 24px; alignment: start;
                                AppearanceSettings { theme-changed(m) => { root.theme-changed(m); } }
                                IntegrationsSettings { }
                            }
                            VerticalLayout {
                                horizontal-stretch: 5; spacing: 24px; alignment: start;
                                SystemControlSettings {
                                    autostart: root.autostart; disable-mpo: root.disable-mpo; fps-cap: root.fps-cap;
                                    shader-quality: root.shader-quality; vsync-mode: root.vsync-mode;
                                    autostart-toggled(v) => { root.autostart = v; root.autostart-toggled(v); }
                                    mpo-toggled(v) => { root.disable-mpo = v; root.mpo-toggled(v); }
                                    fps-cap-changed(v) => { root.fps-cap = v; root.fps-cap-changed(v); }
                                    shader-quality-changed(v) => { root.shader-quality = v; root.shader-quality-changed(v); }
                                    vsync-changed(v) => { root.vsync-mode = v; root.vsync-changed(v); }
                                }
                                InteractivitySettings {
                                    audio-sensitivity: root.audio-sensitivity;
                                    mouse-mode: root.mouse-mode;
                                    mouse-sensitivity: root.mouse-sensitivity;
                                    audio-sensitivity-changed(v) => { root.audio-sensitivity = v; root.audio-sensitivity-changed(v); }
                                    mouse-mode-changed(v) => { root.mouse-mode = v; root.mouse-mode-changed(v); }
                                    mouse-sensitivity-changed(v) => { root.mouse-sensitivity = v; root.mouse-sensitivity-changed(v); }
                                }
                                UpdatesSettings {
                                    version-badge: root.update-version-badge;
                                    update-button-label: root.update-button-label;
                                    update-available: root.update-available;
                                    update-checking: root.update-checking;
                                    update-clicked => { root.check-for-updates(); }
                                    lib-version-badge: root.lib-update-version-badge;
                                    lib-update-button-label: root.lib-update-button-label;
                                    lib-update-available: root.lib-update-available;
                                    lib-update-checking: root.lib-update-checking;
                                    lib-update-clicked => { root.check-for-library-updates(); }
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        // â”€â”€ Narrow: single stacked column â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
                        if !settings-area.two-col : VerticalLayout {
                            spacing: 24px; alignment: start;
                            AppearanceSettings { theme-changed(m) => { root.theme-changed(m); } }
                            SystemControlSettings {
                                autostart: root.autostart; disable-mpo: root.disable-mpo; fps-cap: root.fps-cap;
                                shader-quality: root.shader-quality; vsync-mode: root.vsync-mode;
                                autostart-toggled(v) => { root.autostart = v; root.autostart-toggled(v); }
                                mpo-toggled(v) => { root.disable-mpo = v; root.mpo-toggled(v); }
                                fps-cap-changed(v) => { root.fps-cap = v; root.fps-cap-changed(v); }
                                shader-quality-changed(v) => { root.shader-quality = v; root.shader-quality-changed(v); }
                                vsync-changed(v) => { root.vsync-mode = v; root.vsync-changed(v); }
                            }
                            InteractivitySettings {
                                audio-sensitivity: root.audio-sensitivity;
                                mouse-mode: root.mouse-mode;
                                mouse-sensitivity: root.mouse-sensitivity;
                                audio-sensitivity-changed(v) => { root.audio-sensitivity = v; root.audio-sensitivity-changed(v); }
                                mouse-mode-changed(v) => { root.mouse-mode = v; root.mouse-mode-changed(v); }
                                mouse-sensitivity-changed(v) => { root.mouse-sensitivity = v; root.mouse-sensitivity-changed(v); }
                            }
                            IntegrationsSettings { }
                            UpdatesSettings {
                                    version-badge: root.update-version-badge;
                                    update-button-label: root.update-button-label;
                                    update-available: root.update-available;
                                    update-checking: root.update-checking;
                                    update-clicked => { root.check-for-updates(); }
                                    lib-version-badge: root.lib-update-version-badge;
                                    lib-update-button-label: root.lib-update-button-label;
                                    lib-update-available: root.lib-update-available;
                                    lib-update-checking: root.lib-update-checking;
                                    lib-update-clicked => { root.check-for-library-updates(); }
                                }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // â•گâ•گ Diagnostics tab â•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گâ•گ
            // == Diagnostics tab ===============================================
            if root.active-tab == "diagnostics" : diag-area := Rectangle {
                vertical-stretch: 1;
                // Explicit, equal card widths (content width minus scrollbar gutter,
                // padding and inter-card gaps) so the tiles form an even grid.
                property <length> cw4: (self.width - 106px) / 4;
                property <length> cw2: (self.width - 58px) / 2;
                // Height of the stat-card block (one 150px row, or two stacked).
                property <length> stat-h: root.width >= 1180px ? 150px : 324px;

                ScrollView {
                    VerticalLayout {
                        width: diag-area.width - 26px;
                        padding: 4px; spacing: 24px;

                        // Telemetry stat cards - 4-up on wide windows, 2x2 when narrow.
                        if root.width >= 1180px : HorizontalLayout {
                            spacing: 24px; alignment: start;
                            FpsStatCard { width: diag-area.cw4; fps: root.fps; active: root.engine-active; }
                            StatCard {
                                width: diag-area.cw4;
                                icon: "clock"; icon-bg: #38bdf81f; icon-color: #38bdf8;
                                label: "FRAME TIME"; value: root.engine-active ? "\{Math.round(root.frame-time * 10) / 10}" : "-"; unit: root.engine-active ? "ms" : "";
                            }
                            StatCard {
                                width: diag-area.cw4;
                                icon: "database"; icon-bg: Theme.palette.card-hover; icon-color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                                label: "VRAM USAGE"; value: root.engine-active ? "\{Math.round(root.vram-usage * 10) / 10}" : "0"; unit: "MB";
                            }
                            DebugActionsCard {
                                width: diag-area.cw4; debug-overlay: root.debug-overlay;
                                open-debugger => { root.open-debugger(); }
                                debug-toggled(v) => { root.debug-overlay = v; root.debug-toggled(v); }
                            }
                        }
                        if root.width < 1180px : VerticalLayout {
                            spacing: 24px;
                            HorizontalLayout {
                                spacing: 24px; alignment: start;
                                FpsStatCard { width: diag-area.cw2; fps: root.fps; active: root.engine-active; }
                                StatCard {
                                    width: diag-area.cw2;
                                    icon: "clock"; icon-bg: #38bdf81f; icon-color: #38bdf8;
                                    label: "FRAME TIME"; value: root.engine-active ? "\{Math.round(root.frame-time * 10) / 10}" : "-"; unit: root.engine-active ? "ms" : "";
                                }
                            }
                            HorizontalLayout {
                                spacing: 24px; alignment: start;
                                StatCard {
                                    width: diag-area.cw2;
                                    icon: "database"; icon-bg: Theme.palette.card-hover; icon-color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                                    label: "VRAM USAGE"; value: root.engine-active ? "\{Math.round(root.vram-usage * 10) / 10}" : "0"; unit: "MB";
                                }
                                DebugActionsCard {
                                    width: diag-area.cw2; debug-overlay: root.debug-overlay;
                                    open-debugger => { root.open-debugger(); }
                                    debug-toggled(v) => { root.debug-overlay = v; root.debug-toggled(v); }
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        // Diagnostics log panel.  Its height is the space left below
                        // the stat cards, but never less than 360px - so on a tall
                        // window it fills, and on the small default window it keeps a
                        // readable height that pushes the content past the viewport,
                        // making the outer ScrollView scroll (instead of clipping).
                        Rectangle {
                            min-height: (diag-area.height - diag-area.stat-h - 32px) > 360px
                                      ? (diag-area.height - diag-area.stat-h - 32px) : 360px;
                            border-radius: 24px;
                            background: Theme.palette.card; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                            VerticalLayout {
                                padding: 24px; spacing: 20px;
                                HorizontalLayout {
                                    spacing: 14px;
                                    Rectangle {
                                        width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px; background: Theme.palette.accent.with-alpha(0.1);
                                        Icon { name: "terminal"; size: 20px; color: Theme.palette.accent; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                                    }
                                    VerticalLayout {
                                        horizontal-stretch: 1; alignment: center; spacing: 2px;
                                        Text { text: "Engine Diagnostics Log"; font-family: Theme.font-headline; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                                        Text { text: "Real-time Strata log output"; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; }
                                    }
                                    Rectangle {
                                        width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
                                        background: cp-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
                                        animate background { duration: 150ms; }
                                        Icon { name: "copy"; size: 16px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; x: (parent.width - self.width)/2; y: (parent.height - self.height)/2; }
                                        cp-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.copy-logs(); } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                                    }
                                }
                                log-box := Rectangle {
                                    vertical-stretch: 1; border-radius: 16px; clip: true;
                                    background: Theme.palette.background;
                                    border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                                    ScrollView {
                                        VerticalLayout {
                                            width: log-box.width - 28px;
                                            padding: 16px; spacing: 8px; alignment: start;
                                            for entry in root.logs : HorizontalLayout {
                                                spacing: 14px;
                                                Text { text: entry.time; font-family: Theme.font-code; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
                                                       color: Theme.palette.text-muted; width: 66px; }
                                                LogLevelBadge { level: entry.level; y: 1px; }
                                                Text { text: entry.message; font-family: Theme.font-code; font-size: 11px;
                                                       color: Theme.palette.text; horizontal-stretch: 1; wrap: word-wrap; }
                                            }
                                            if root.logs.length == 0 : Text {
                                                text: "No log output yet.";
                                                font-family: Theme.font-code; font-size: 11px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted;
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // ── Toast overlay ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    // Floats above everything, anchored bottom-right. Plain Rectangles don't
    // grab pointer input, so only the toast close buttons are interactive - the
    // rest of the UI underneath stays fully usable.
    Rectangle {
        width: 100%; height: 100%;
        VerticalLayout {
            alignment: end;
            HorizontalLayout {
                alignment: end;
                padding: 24px;
                VerticalLayout {
                    spacing: 10px;
                    for t[i] in root.toasts : ToastCard {
                        title: t.title;
                        description: t.description;
                        destructive: t.destructive;
                        dismissed => { root.toast-dismissed(t.id); }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // ── "Name your movie wallpaper" dialog (opened on .mp4 import) ────────────
    if root.show-video-name-dialog : Rectangle {
        background: #000000aa;
        TouchArea { clicked => { root.show-video-name-dialog = false; } }
        Rectangle {
            width: 400px; height: vid-name-col.preferred-height + 48px;
            x: (parent.width - self.width) / 2;
            y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;
            background: Theme.palette.card;
            border-radius: 16px; border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
            drop-shadow-blur: 40px; drop-shadow-color: #00000066;
            TouchArea {}
            vid-name-col := VerticalLayout {
                padding: 24px; spacing: 14px;
                // Prefill with the file name each time the dialog opens.
                init => { vid-name-input.text = root.video-name-default; }
                Text { text: "Name your movie wallpaper"; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: Theme.palette.text; }
                Text { text: "Leave blank to use the video's file name."; font-size: 12px; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; wrap: word-wrap; }
                vid-name-input := BlueInput { placeholder: "My Movie Wallpaper"; }
                HorizontalLayout {
                    spacing: 12px; alignment: end;
                    Rectangle {
                        width: 96px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px;
                        background: vid-cancel-ta.has-hover ? Theme.palette.card-hover : transparent;
                        border-width: 1px; border-color: Theme.palette.border;
                        Text { text: "CANCEL"; color: Theme.palette.text-muted; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px;
                               horizontal-alignment: center; vertical-alignment: center; }
                        vid-cancel-ta := TouchArea { clicked => { root.show-video-name-dialog = false; } mouse-cursor: pointer; }
                    }
                    PillButton {
                        width: 160px; btn-height: 44px; text: "IMPORT"; icon: "save";
                        clicked => {
                            root.video-import-confirmed(vid-name-input.text);
                            root.show-video-name-dialog = false;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
